traveling%2C%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20I%20spent%20varied%20from%20place%20to%20place.%20For%20example%2C%20when%20I%20was%20in%20Bali%2C%20my%20money%20stretched%20a%20bit%20further%20than%20it%20did%20in%20America.%20But%20when%20I%20was%20in%20Japan%2C%20I%20had%20to%20budget%20my%20money%20carefully.%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20fixed%20expenses%20like%20food%2C%20transportation%2C%20and%20accommodations%20like%20my%20Airbnb%2C%20but%20I%20never%20knew%20how%20much%20I%20would%20actually%20be%20spending%20until%20I%20got%20to%20a%20certain%20location.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20finances%20fluctuated%20because%20each%20country%20was%20so%20different%2C%20and%20I%20also%20wasn't%20the%20best%20at%20budgeting.%20Since%20it%20was%20my%20first%20time%20traveling%20abroad%2C%20there%20was%20a%20big%20learning%20curve%2C%20especially%20surrounding%20money%20and%20knowing%20how%20much%20I%20could%20spend.%20Traveling%20abroad%20was%20new%20to%20me%2C%20and%20while%20managing%20my%20money%20in%20foreign%20countries%20was%20hard%2C%20I%20learned%20a%20lot%20from%20the%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bhandari%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6529966755f52b01b35f75d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBhandari%20went%20to%20Italy%2C%20Spain%2C%20New%20York%20and%20more%20living%20her%20dream%20as%20a%20nomad.%3Cp%3ECelina%20Bhandari%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20I%20had%20a%20hard%20time%20maintaining%20friendships%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20met%20so%20many%20people%20when%20I%20was%20a%20digital%20nomad%2C%20but%20because%20I%20was%20always%20moving%2C%20the%20people%20I%20met%20couldn't%20be%20consistent%20friends.%20I'd%20make%20friends%2C%20but%20when%20I'd%20leave%20for%20another%20country%20or%20place%2C%20those%20friendships%20became%20harder%20to%20maintain.%20Using%20social%20media%20to%20stay%20in%20contact%20helps%20a%20b