%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20said%2C%20I've%20always%20found%20routines%20and%20habits%20to%20be%20important%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20work.%20Although%20I%20wanted%20to%20advance%20myself%20in%20my%20career%2C%20not%20having%20a%20stable%20routine%20and%20even%20a%20consistent%20time%20zone%20felt%20challenging.%20Since%20my%20clients%20were%20based%20in%20the%20US%2C%20I%20was%20constantly%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20right%20time%20to%20take%20phone%20calls%20and%20meetings%20that%20wasn't%20at%20midnight%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222047%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Celina%20Bhandari%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6529875b6561dd877e7a635f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221535%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlthough%20moving%20from%20place%20to%20place%20felt%20like%20a%20dream%20in%20many%20ways%20it%20was%20also%20hard%20not%20knowing%20where%20she%20would%20be%20next.%3Cp%3ECelina%20Bhandari%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E4.%20It%20was%20hard%20figuring%20out%20where%20to%20go%20next%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20finding%20a%20place%2C%20I%20constantly%20asked%20myself%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20next%3F%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWhat%20city%20should%20I%20go%20to%3F%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWhat%20apartment%20should%20I%20choose%3F%26quot%3B%20While%20that%20may%20sound%20exciting%2C%20after%20a%20while%20it%20becomes%20tiring%2C%20especially%20for%20an%20indecisive%20person%20like%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20back%20and%20forth%20trying%20to%20make%20these%20decisions.%20The%20uncertainty%20made%20the%20process%20challenging%2C%20and%20the%20competition%20of%20apartment%20hunting%20was%20tough.%20I'd%20always%20search%20Facebook%20for%20my%20next%20place%2C%20but%20the%20apartments%20would%20go%20rather%20quickly%2C%20especially%20because%20I%20was%20looking%20at%20places%20that%20were%20on%20the%20cheaper%20side.%20There%20were%20times%20when%