rchasing%20Managers'%20Index.%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20wonderful%20tool.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E3.%20%26quot%3BI%20find%20comfort%20in%20looking%20at%20the%20plunging%20demand%20for%20cardboard%20boxes.%20I've%20been%20referring%20to%20this%20as%20a%20'cardboard%20box%20recession'%20because%20things%20that%20are%20manufactured%20and%20shipped%20tend%20to%20go%20in%20a%20box%2C%20and%20because%20demand%20for%20corrugated%20fiberboard%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20what%20most%20cardboard%20boxes%20are%20made%20from%20%E2%80%94%20has%20fallen%20just%20like%20it%20did%20in%20past%20recessions.%20So%2C%20literally%2C%20cardboard%20boxes%20are%20in%20a%20recession.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E4.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20a%20florist%20and%20you%20were%20thinking%20about%20buying%20that%20extra%20truck%20and%20staffing%20it%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20do%20that%20now.%20Banks%20are%20demanding%20more%20collateral%2C%20higher%20rates%2C%20qualifying%20fewer%20borrowers.%20So%2C%20things%20are%20getting%20tighter.%26quot%3B%20(Kleintop%20was%20highlighting%20that%20many%20small%20businesses%20are%20finding%20it%20harder%20to%20borrow.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E5.%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20travel%20and%20entertainment%20have%20been%20strong%20%E2%80%94%20just%20ask%20Taylor%20Swift.%20It's%20been%20big%2C%20but%20it's%20coming%20down.%20We've%20heard%20that%20from%20airlines.%20You're%20seeing%20higher%20vacancies%20at%20hotels%2C%20more%20open%20reservations%20on%20OpenTable.com.%20I%20live%20three%20miles%20from%20Walt%20Disney%20World%20here%20in%20Florida.%20You%20know%20what%3F%20You%20can%20actually%20get%20on%20Space%20Mountain%20lately.%20You%20don't%20have%20to%20wait%20two%20hours.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E6.%20%26quot%3BAll%20these%20signs%20are%20indicating%20that%20we're%20seeing%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20slowdown%20in%20the%20services%20sector.%20That's%20important%20because%20there%20are%2010%20times%20as%20many%20services%20jobs%20as%20manufacturing%20jobs%20in%20the%20US.%2