y%20work%20from%20an%20office%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20these%20benefits%2C%20I%20always%20thought%20that%20working%20remotely%20would%20be%20incredible%2C%20so%20when%20my%20boyfriend%20took%20an%20assignment%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fim-a-travel-nurse-make-great-money-live-across-america-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etravel%20nurse%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March%2C%20I%20asked%20my%20company%20if%20I%20could%20work%20remotely%20so%20I%20could%20travel%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20been%20working%20in%20medical%20staffing%20for%20three%20years%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20really%20good%20about%20my%20job.%20But%20I%20was%20looking%20forward%20to%20traveling%20with%20my%20boyfriend%20on%20his%20new%20adventure%20%E2%80%94%20plus%2C%20I'd%20cut%20out%20a%2030-minute%20commute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20boss%20was%20understanding%20and%20said%20yes.%20I%20couldn't%20wait%20to%20enjoy%20all%20the%20benefits%20of%20flexible%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20here's%20what%20I%20didn't%20see%20online%3A%20Working%20from%20home%20is%20a%20lonely%20experience%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20never%20knew%20how%20much%20I%20depended%20on%20the%20social%20and%20emotional%20stimulation%20of%20the%20office%20until%20I%20didn't%20have%20it.%20Suddenly%2C%20it%20was%20just%20me%20by%20myself%20the%20entire%20day%20while%20my%20boyfriend%20was%20at%20work.%20I%20would%20sit%20in%20front%20of%20my%20computer%20in%20our%20rental%20house%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstaying-connected-while-working-from-home-amid-the-coronavirus-crisis-2020-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emiss%20my%20coworkers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20see%20it%20coming%20at%20all.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-to-be-an-introvert-and-what-everyone-gets-wrong-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EI'm%20an%20introvert%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20love%20being%20by%20myself%2C%20but%20being%20alone%20all%20the%20time%20and%20knowing%20my%20coworkers%20were%20together%20was%20really%20hard.%20I%20didn't%20realize%20how%20much%20I%20feed%20off%20being%20around%20other%20people%20and%20making%20them%20happy.%20It%20really%20took%20a%20toll%20on%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20started%20waking%20up%205%20minutes%20before%20work%20and%20bringing%20my%20laptop%20to%20bed%20to%20start%20at%208%20a.m.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wouldn't%20even%20get%20out%20of%20bed%20some%20days%2C%20which%20was%20so%20different%20from%20when%20I%20worked%20in%20the%20office%20and%20I%20would%20wake%20up%20at%205%20a.m.%20feeling%20so%20put%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20hard%20to%20feel%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-quiet-quitting-work-ethic-millennials-money-struggles-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Einvested%20in%20my%20job%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20working%20remotely.%20It%20made%20me%20sad%20because%20I%20do%20love%20learning%2C%20working%20hard%2C%20and%20trying%20my%20best%2C%20but%20when%20I'm%20working%20from%20home%2C%20it%20just%20doesn't%20come%20as%20naturally%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20lose%20my%20productivity%2C%20though.%20It's%20fascinating%20how%20much%20work%20you%20can%20get%20done%20when%20you're%20in%20a%20room%20by%20yourself%20and%20not%20distracted%20by%20coworkers%20and%20a%20lively%20office%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20nurture%20your%20relationships%20with%20coworkers%20when%20you're%20not%20around%20them%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20same%20to%20chat%20over%20messenger%20or%20video%20conference%20over%20Zoom.%20You%20don't%20get%20to%20establish%20the%20same%20connections%20you%20would%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20to%20FaceTime%20with%20my%20coworkers%20occasionally%2