each%20visit%2C%20lines%20at%20lunch%20and%20dinner%20snake%20to%20the%20back%20of%20the%20restaurant%20and%20wrap%20around%20the%20dining%20room.%20According%20to%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ftiktokers-claim-downfall-of-chipotle-rise-of-cava-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20viral%20video%20by%20a%20TikTok%20influencer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Chipotle%20%26quot%3Bdoesn't%20hit%20the%20way%20it%20used%20to%26quot%3B%20with%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20set%20out%20to%20compare%20Cava%20and%20Chipotle%20in%20a%20head-to-head%20battle.%20To%20keep%20it%20simple%2C%20I%20compared%20Chipotle's%20burritos%20and%20bowls%20to%20Cava's%20pitas%20and%20bowls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20tight%20race.%20Ultimately%2C%20fate%20helped%20me%20crown%20a%20champion.%20Here's%20what%20I%20discovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(Note%3A%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPrices%20reflect%20purchases%20made%20at%20Chipotle%20and%20Cava%20stores%20in%20Orange%20County%2C%20California.%20Prices%20may%20vary%20where%20you%20live.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20visited%20a%20Chipotle%20in%20a%20college%20town%20near%20my%20house.%20I%20stood%20around%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20minutes%20before%20someone%20decided%20to%20help%20me.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nancy%20Luna%20waits%20for%20someone%20to%20help%20her%20at%20Chipotle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652eedb296f7540cd05ed294%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInsider%20reporter%20Nancy%20Luna%20waits%20for%20someone%20to%20help%20her%20at%20Chipotle.%3Cp%3EInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spotted%20at%20least%20three%20people%20working%20behind%20the%20counter.%20They%20were%20either%20prepping%20food%20or%20assembling%20meals%20for%20digital%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETakeout%20and%20delivery%20orders%20are%20big%20business%20for%20Chipotle.%20In%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchipotle-ceo-brian-niccol-shares-playbook-for-growing-digital-sales-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChipotle's%20digital%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20surpassed%20%243%20billion%20in%20revenue.%20In%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%202023%2C%20digital%20sales%20represented%2038%25%20of%20the%20chain's%20food%20and%20beverage%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20that's%20no%20excuse%20for%20not%20having%20an%20employee%20immediately%20available%20to%20help%20a%20customer%20waiting%20in%20line.%20Especially%20as%20I%20was%20the%20only%20person%20in%20line%20at%20dinnertime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEvery%20time%20I%20visit%20Chipotle%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20hardly%20anyone%20in%20line.%20What's%20up%20with%20that%3F%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22No%20lines%20at%20Chipotle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652efc1abe9edfa8eda3449d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhat%20happened%20to%20all%20the%20long%20lines%20at%20Chipotle%3F%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20in-restaurant%20visits%20to%20Chipotle%20don't%20reflect%20a%20lack%20of%20popularity%20for%20the%20chain.%20Chipotle%20is%20still%20a%20hot%20brand.%20In%20June%202023%2C%20visits%20were%20up%20on%20average%208.4%25%20per%20Chipotle%20store%20compared%20to%20June%202022%2C%20according%20to%20data%20by%20Placer.ai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20company%20increased%20its%20revenue%20by%2014.4%25%20to%20%248.6%20billion.%20I%20must%20be%20visiting%20stores%20that%20cater%20to%20a%20mobile-order%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECava%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20always%20has%20long%20lines.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Long%20lines%20at%20Cava.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652f0931211def8ed837b8dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECava%20always%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20long%20line%20when%20I%20visit.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20visited%20Cava%20about%20four%20times%20over%20the%20past%20year.%20At%20lunch%20and%20dinner%2C%20each%20location%20commands%20crowds.%20And%20like%20the%20early%20days%20of%20Chipotle%2C%20customers%20don't%20seem%20to%20mind%20waiting%20in%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EChipotle%20prices%20its%20bowls%20by%20the%20type%20of%20protein%20you%20select.%20I%20ordered%20mine%20with%20carne%20asada%2C%20a%20premium%20protein%20available%20for%20a%20limited%20time%20only.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Approximately%2065%25%20of%20all%20Chipotle%20digital%20orders%20are%20bowls%20or%20salads.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652efe46211def8ed837b036%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApproximately%2065%25%20of%20all%20Chipotle%20digital%20orders%20are%20bowls%20or%20salads.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20carne%20asada's%20third%20time%20on%20the%20Chipotle%20menu%20after%20first%20debuting%20as%20a%20limited-time%20offer%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fan%20favorite%20is%20top%20sirloin%20and%20tri-tip%20steak%20strips%20seasoned%20with%20cumin%2C%20coriander%2C%20and%20oregano.%20It%20comes%20at%20a%20premium%20price%20%E2%80%93%20%2411.85.%20Other%20proteins%20on%20the%20menu%20ranged%20in%20price%20from%20%248.85%20to%20%2410.60.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20used%20to%20think%20the%20topping%20options%20at%20Chipotle%20were%20plentiful.%20But%20after%20eating%20at%20Cava%2C%20the%20Chipotle%20choices%20seem%20boring%20and%20scarce.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Someone%20dolloping%20guacamole%20on%20a%20Chipotle%20bowl.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F641201588215b5001814838d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20you%20eliminate%20the%20four%20salsa%20options%2C%20the%20remaining%20free%20toppings%20at%20Chipotle%20are%20sour%20cream%2C%20shredded%20cheese%2C%20fajita%20veggies%2C%20and%20romaine%20lettuce.%20That's%20not%20that%20much%20compared%20to%20Cava.%3Cp%3EJoe%20Raedle%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20selecting%20your%20beans%2C%20rice%2C%20and%20protein%2C%20Chipotle%20offers%20eight%20toppings%20for%20free%20to%20customize%20your%20bowl%3A%20fresh%20tomato%20salsa%2C%20roasted%20chili%20corn%20salsa%2C%20tomatillo-green%20chili%20salsa%2C%20tomatillo-red%20salsa%2C%20sour%20cream%2C%20shredded%20cheese%2C%20fajita%20veggies%2C%20and%20romaine%20lettuce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20chose%20all%20the%20free%20options%20except%20the%20tomatillo-red%20salsa%2C%20which%20is%20too%20spicy%20for%20my%20palate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20can%20add%20guacamole%20(%242.65)%20and%20queso%20blanco%20(%241.70)%20for%20an%20upcharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20eliminate%20the%20salsa%20options%2C%20there%20are%20only%20four%20free%20topping%20choices%20at%20Chipotle.%20That's%20underwhelming%20when%20compared%20to%20Cava.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20I%20ordered%20along%20the%20assembly%20line%2C%20I%20noticed%20all%20the%20food%20bins%20were%20practically%20empty.%20I%20got%20the%20last%20scoopful%20of%20many%20items%2C%20including%20the%20carne.%20asada%2C%20which%20wasn't%20a%20good%20sign%20that%20I%20was%20getting%20fresh%20products.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221473%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chipotle%20burrito%20and%20bowl.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652f003396f7540cd05eed01%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221105%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInsider%20food%20correspondent%20Nancy%20Luna%20ordered%20a%20custom%20bowl%20and%20burrito%20at%20Chipotle%2C%20and%C2%A0%20compared%20it%20to%20Cava's%20bowl%20and%20pita.%3Cp%3EInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Chipotle%20bowl%20did%20not%20meet%20my%20expectations%20because%20the%20ingredients%20didn't%20taste%20fresh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chain%20describes%20the%20carne%20asada%20as%20juicy%20strips%20of%20steak%20seasoned%20with%20spices%20and%20topped%20with%20a%20squeeze%20of%20lime.%20But%20I%20couldn't%20taste%20any%20of%20those%20craveable%20flavors.%20The%20steak%20was%20dry%20and%20lukewarm%20to%20the%20touch%2C%20underscoring%20my%20suspicions%20that%20I%20was%20getting%20the%20dregs%20of%20the%20carne%20asada%20sitting%20in%20the%20bin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20bowl%20experience%20at%20Cava%20was%20quite%20different.%20I%20was%20overwhelmed%20with%20the%20variety%20of%20options.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20customized%20bowl%20from%20Cava.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652f00d9211def8ed837b223%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENancy%20Luna%20tried%20Cava's%20fresh%20lemonade%20beverages%20along%20with%20her%20bowl.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Chipotle%20has%20two%20base%20grain%20options%20(white%20or%20brown%20rice)%2C%20Cava%20offers%20nine%20different%20choices%20of%20grains%20and%20greens.%20Almost%20all%20of%20them%20are%20irresistible%2C%20making%20it%20hard%20to%20choose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECava's%20base%20choices%20are%20black%20lentils%2C%20saffron%20basmati%20rice%2C%20brown%20rice%2C%20arugula%2C%20Supergreens%20(a%20blend%20of%20raw%20cabbage%2C%20Brussels%20sprouts%2C%20broccoli%2C%20and%20kale)%2C%20baby%20spinach%2C%20romaine%2C%20Splendidgreens%20(a%20mix%20of%20chopped%20romaine%2C%20radicchio%2C%20escarole%2C%20chicory%20endive%2C%20and%20cabbage)%20and%20RightRice.%20The%20latter%20is%20a%20high-protein%20veggie%20rice%20available%20for%20a%20%241.35%20upcharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20ingredients%20are%20super%20appealing%20to%20anyone%20looking%20for%20healthy%20high-fiber%20choices%20in%20their%20diet.%20I've%20tasted%20nearly%20all%20of%20these%20options%20except%20the%20spinach.%20I'm%20not%20a%20fan%20of%20Popeye's%20fave%20greens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20RightRice%20is%20a%20solid%2C%20lower-carb%20grain%20that's%20better%20in%20taste%20and%20texture%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fchipotle-new-cauliflower-rice-taste-test-review-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChipotle's%20cilantro-lime%20cauliflower%20rice%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20alt-rice%20is%20no%20longer%20on%20the%20menu%20after%20launching%20nationwide%20for%20a%20limited%20time%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECava%20knows%20its%20choices%20are%20tempting%2C%20as%20the%20chain%20allows%20you%20to%20choose%20two%20options%20as%20one%20base.%20I%20chose%20black%20lentils%20and%20brown%20rice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EUnlike%20Chipotle%2C%20the%20topping%20options%20at%20Cava%20are%20dreamy%20and%20craveworthy.%20That%E2%80%99s%20probably%20why%20the%20lines%20get%20clogged%20because%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20of%20tempting%20choices%20to%20select.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cava%20offers%20plentiful%20topping%20options.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652f023696f7540cd05eee63%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECava%20offers%20plentiful%20topping%20options.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECava's%20main%20entree%20options%20include%20harissa%20honey%20chicken%2C%20spicy%20lamb%20meatballs%2C%20grilled%20chicken%2C%20braised%20lamb%2C%20spicy%20falafel%2C%20falafel%2C%20and%20roasted%20vegetables.%20Customers%20can%20choose%20one%20main%2C%20or%20two%20with%20the%20portion%20sizes%20split%20in%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20chose%20the%20