0crazy-good%20ingredients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWinner%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20Cava%20bowl%20wins%20on%20value%2C%20taste%2C%20and%20freshness.%20Even%20though%20Cava%20is%20more%20expensive%20than%20Chipotle%2C%20I%20am%20willing%20to%20pay%20a%20couple%20of%20extra%20bucks%20for%20the%20sheer%20volume%20of%20flavors%20packed%20in%20the%20chain's%20bowls.%20It's%20a%20better%20bang%20for%20my%20buck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhile%20Cava%E2%80%99s%20bowls%20are%20a%20thing%20of%20beauty%2C%20their%20pitas%20are%20ugly%20and%20messy.%20You%20need%20a%20smock%20to%20eat%20these%20bulging%20wraps.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cava's%20pita%20wraps%20are%20bigger%20than%20Chipotle's%20burritos%2C%20but%20messy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652f05b7211def8ed837b692%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECava's%20pita%20wraps%20are%20bigger%20than%20Chipotle's%20burritos%2C%20but%20messy.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20choose%20a%20lot%20of%20toppings%20for%20a%20bowl%20at%20Cava%2C%20it%20doesn't%20impact%20the%20presentation%20of%20the%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20when%20you%20select%20numerous%20toppings%20for%20the%20pita%2C%20you%20end%20up%20building%20a%20messy%20monster%20of%20a%20wrap.%20When%20biting%20into%20the%20unwieldy%20pita%2C%20ingredients%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20wrap%20ooze%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20pita%20is%20in%20a%20constant%20state%20of%20falling%20apart.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20handheld%20meal%20that%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20hold.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cava's%20pita%20wraps%20are%20messy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652f0550be9edfa8eda34c08%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECava's%20bulging%20pita%20wraps%20are%20mes