riests-freed-sent-to-vatican%2Famp_articleshow%2F104550307.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Wagah%20Flagpole%20Rivalry%20Is%20the%20Latest%20Competitive%20Sport%20Between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19131739%2Fgodwin-angeline-benjo-pa1LfQ4Cj3w-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20bizarre%20%E2%80%98flagpole%E2%80%99%20rivalry%2C%20currently%20raging%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20along%20their%20solitary%20official%20land-border%20crossing%20at%20Wagah%2C%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20long%20and%20ever%20widening%20list%20of%20competitive%20sports%20between%20the%20antagonistic%20neighbours.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20newly%20erected%20418%20feet%20high%20flagpole%20at%20Wagah%2C%20likely%20to%20be%20formally%20inaugurated%20and%20capped%20with%20a%20flag%20on%20Thursday%20by%20Union%20transport%20minister%20Nitin%20Gadkari%2C%20stands%2018%20feet%20higher%20than%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20in%20this%20enduring%20%E2%80%98one-up%20flagpole-ship%E2%80%99%20between%20the%20two%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECosting%20around%20Rs%203.5%20crore%2C%20this%20flagpole%20replaces%20the%20360-foot%20high%20one%20India%20had%20first%20installed%20at%20the%20same%20location%20in%20March%202017.%20In%20response%2C%20Pakistan%20had%20mounted%20a%20400%20feet%20tall%20flagstaff%20a%20few%20months%20later%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20latest%20Indian%20retaliation%20of%20installing%20one%20even%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20a%20reply%20that%20is%20certain%20to%20follow%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20according%20to%20that%20country%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftribune.com.pk%2Fstory%2F2410868%2Findo-pak-battle-of-tallest-flag-at-wagah-border-to-start-once-again%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EExpress%20Tribune%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20now%20expected%20to%20raise%20its%20border%20flag%20%E2%80%98even%20higher%20than%20that%20of%20its%20arch%20rival%E2%80%99%20and%20best%20the%20418%20foot%20high%20flagpole%20in%20this%20seemingly%20endless%20%E2%80%93%20and%20senseless%20%E2%80%93%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20new%20flagpole%20has%20been%20a%20source%20of%20discomfiture%20for%20locals%20and%20visitors%20for%20many%20months%20now%2C%20as%20it%20has%20been%20without%20a%20flag%2C%20while%20the%20Pakistani%20standard%20of%20the%20Star%20and%20Crescent%20dominates%20the%20landscape%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20border%2C%20visible%20for%20long%20distances.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20see%20the%20Pakistani%20flag%208-9%20km%20from%20the%20border%20and%20feel%20disheartened%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wagah%20farmer%20Jaspal%20Singh%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchandigarh%2Fnations-tallest-flagpole-at-attari-awaits-tricolour%2Farticleshow%2F104355991.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently.%20We%20may%20have%20the%20higher%20flagpole%2C%20but%20no%20flag%2C%20which%20is%20embarrassing%2C%20he%20added.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20media%20reports%20%E2%80%93%20albeit%20questionable%20%E2%80%93%20from%20either%20side%20of%20Wagah%20have%20claimed%20that%20the%20respective%20flags%20can%2C%20on%20a%20clear%20day%2C%20be%20seen%20from%20Amritsar%20and%20Lahore%20that%20are%2031%20km%20and%2022%20km%20respectively%20from%20the%20frontier.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOfficials%20from%20the%20National%20Highways%20Authority%20of%20India%2C%20that%20built%20the%20flagpole%2C%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20missing%20flag%2C%20but%20privately%20conceded%20that%20some%20%E2%80%98technical%20issues%E2%80%99%20had%20hindered%20its%20hoisting.%20They%20claimed%20that%20these%20had%20now%20been%20resolved%20and%20that%20the%20tricolour%20would%20imminently%20be%20raised%20atop%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20earlier%20faced%20problems%20with%20its%20120%20feet%20wide%20flags%2C%20as%20each%20one%20costing%20around%20Rs%2015%20lakh%2C%20had%20suffered%20tears%20within%20a%20few%20weeks%20of%20being%20hoisted%20due%20to%20blistering%20winds%20that%20swept%20the%20area.%20It%20was%20further%20estimated%20that%20it%20would%20annually%20cost%20India%20nearly%20Rs%202%20crore%20to%20replace%20them%2C%20as%20domestic%20regulations%20stipulate%20that%20a%20damaged%20flag%20cannot%20be%20flown.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20officials%20had%20suggested%20the%20installation%20of%20a%20smaller%20flag%20to%20reduce%20wear%20and%20tear%2C%20but%20the%20Border%20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%20that%20mans%20Wagah%20vetoed%20this%20proposal%20and%20insisted%20on%20displaying%20one%20that%20was%20prominently%20visible%20for%20extended%20stretches%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20rivalry%20between%20the%20nuclear-armed%20neighbours%20extends%20well%20beyond%20flagpoles%20into%20multiple%20facets%20on%20either%20side%20of%20their%20volatile%20frontier.%20It%20stretches%20further%20than%20diplomatically%20and%20strategically%20finessing%20each%20other%20%E2%80%93%20for%20example%20by%20acquiring%20more%20sophisticated%20materiel%20than%20the%20other%20and%20even%20conducting%20tit-for-tat%20nuclear%20tests%20(Pakistan%20undertook%20six%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20five%20in%20May%201998)%20%E2%80%93%20to%20mundane%2C%20everyday%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEach%20country%20claims%20to%20grow%20a%20greater%20variety%20of%20sweeter%20mangoes%2C%20melons%20and%20grapes%20than%20the%20other%2C%20produce%20better%20music%20and%20television%20programmes%20and%20even%20entertain%2C%20dress%20and%20keep%20a%20better%20table%20than%20those%20across%20the%20border.%20Pakistanis%20claim%20Indians%20are%20far%20less%20hospitable%20and%20pride%20themselves%20on%20a%20keener%20sense%20of%20humour%20and%20irreverence%2C%20higher%20intellect%20and%20finer%20sense%20of%20%3Cem%3Etehzeeb%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20etiquette%20than%20their%20neighbours.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20one%20domain%20in%20which%20most%20Pakistanis%20willingly%2C%20but%20grudgingly%2C%20accept%20Indian%20supremacy%20is%20Bollywood%2C%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20movie%20bazaar.%20They%20reluctantly%20acknowledge%20that%20Lollywood%2C%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20forever%20nascent%20film%20industry%20based%20out%20of%20Lahore%2C%20is%20a%20poor%20imitation%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20film%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20to%20be%20cowed%2C%20they%20reassure%20themselves%20by%20pointing%20out%20that%20for%20decades%20a%20majority%20of%20Bollywood%E2%80%99s%20icons%20have%20been%20Muslims%20like%20the%20recently%20deceased%20Yusuf%20Khan%2C%20better%20known%20as%20Dilip%20Kumar%2C%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%2C%20Salman%20Khan%2C%20Amjad%20Khan%20and%20Aamir%20Khan.%20Muslim%20Bollywood%20actresses%20like%20Katrina%20Kaif%20and%20Shabana%20Azmi%20too%20are%20household%20names%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20with%20most%20of%20their%20films%20hits%20in%20that%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20sides%20believe%20that%20their%20sporting%20prowess%20in%20cricket%20and%20hockey%2C%20which%20Indians%20and%20Pakistanis%20had%20played%20with%20dexterity%20as%20one%20before%20independence%2C%20is%20superior%20to%20the%20other.%20Similar%20sentiments%20applied%20to%20esoteric%20games%20like%20polo%20and%20equestrian%20sports%20like%20tent-pegging%20and%20show%20jumping.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECricket%20matches%20between%20the%20neighbours%20are%20particularly%20tense%20events%20%E2%80%93%20as%20was%20apparent%20over%20the%20weekend%20%E2%80%93%20almost%20mirroring%20their%20military%20rivalry%2C%20as%20the%20losing%20side%20faces%20the%20ire%20of%20millions%20of%20fans%20in%20either%20country.%20Over%20years%2C%20this%20has%20often%20turned%20nasty%20for%20the%20losing%20team%20returning%20home%2C%20especially%20in%20Pakistan.%20The%20victorious%20cricketing%20or%20hockey%20side%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20lauded%20and%20lavished%20with%20accolades%20and%20financial%20rewards%20for%20having%20bested%20the%20%E2%80%98enemy%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20rivalry%20between%20Indians%20and%20Pakistanis%20arises%20not%20so%20much%20from%20being%20different%2C%20but%20from%20being%20somewhat%20similar%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20former%20Indian%20diplomat%20previously%20posted%20in%20Islamabad.%20This%2C%20he%20added%2C%20locked%20them%20into%20an%20unending%20competitive%20cycle%20to%20outdo%20one%20another%20in%20all%20spheres%20and%20to%20portray%20the%20other%20side%20as%20lesser%20beings%20in%20this%20complex%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20late%20foreign%2C%20defence%20and%20finance%20minister%20Jaswant%20Singh%20felt%20similarly%2C%20declaring%20that%20both%20countries%20shared%20a%20common%20heritage%20which%20they%20went%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20deny%20for%20political%2C%20nationalistic%20and%20religious%20reasons.%20%E2%80%9CIndia%2C%20Pakistan%20(and%20Bangladesh)%20are%20from%20the%20same%20womb%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20stated%20some%20years%20ago%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20had%20an%20%E2%80%98intrinsic%E2%80%99%20bonding%20at%20a%20time%20when%20such%20sentiments%20were%20considered%20%E2%80%98unacceptable%E2%80%99%20to%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20aggressive%20competition%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20however%2C%20showcases%20itself%20conspicuously%20at%20Wagah%2C%20where%20the%20flagpole%20competition%20is%20raging%2C%20when%20impeccably%20turned-out%20border%20guards%20lower%20their%20respective%20flags%20daily%20at%20sunset.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpecially%20instructed%20BSF%20personnel%2C%20selected%20for%20their%20height%2C%20fierce%20moustaches%20and%20military%20bearing%2C%20and%20similarly%20recruited%20but%20salwar-and-kameez%20sporting%20Pakistan%20Rangers%2C%20try%20and%20outdo%20one%20another%20in%20marching%2C%20pirouetting%20and%20screaming%20ear-splitting%20commands%2C%20as%20they%20go%20about%20their%20flag%20lowering.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETheir%20spectacular%20theatrics%20that%20take%20place%20in%20amphitheatre-like%20surroundings%2C%20backed%20by%20robust%20commentary%20from%20accomplished%20comperes%20and%20patriotic%20songs%2C%20are%20lustily%20cheered%20by%20thousands%20of%20spectators%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20frontier.%20Over%20years%2C%20these%20daily%20performances%20for%20which%20tickets%20are%20sold%20have%20become%20hugely%20popular%2C%20and%20are%20rated%20highly%20on%20the%20tourist%20circuit%20in%20both%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20border%20gates%20shut%20at%20sunset%2C%20Pakistani%20and%20Indian%20nationals%2C%20separated%20by%20a%20few%20hundred%20yards%20of%20no-man%E2%80%99s%20land%2C%20shout%20out%20to%20each%20other%20extolling%20the%20performance%20of%20their%20border%20guards%20as%20well%20as%20their%20overall%20superiority.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697704248000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19131739%2Fgodwin-angeline-benjo-pa1LfQ4Cj3w-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fwagah-flagpole-rivalry-is-the-latest-competitive-sport-between-india-and-pakistan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%20newly%20erected%20418%20feet%20high%20flagpole%20at%20Wagah%20stands%2018%20feet%20higher%20than%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20in%20this%20enduring%20%E2%80%98one-up%20flagpole-ship%E2%80%99%20between%20the%20two%20sides.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fwagah-flagpole-rivalry-is-the-latest-competitive-sport-between-india-and-pakistan%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Take%20inspiration%20from%20Kajol%20for%20Navratri%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697704200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104544470%2Cimgsize-56166.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fent