%20shipping%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224436%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Five%20Amazon%20packages%20are%20stacked%20in%20two%20piles%20in%20front%20of%20a%20wooden%20door.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652cf9156561dd877e7b11d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223327%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EXavi%20Lopez%2FSOPA%20Images%2FLightRocket%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EWith%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-private-label-boss-movessupply-chain-role-role-2023-10%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20dropshipping%20model%2C%20your%20business%20is%20the%20forward-facing%20party%20customers%20see.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20third%20party%20handles%20the%20physical%20logistics.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EYou%20make%20money%20by%20setting%20a%20higher%20price%20for%20customers%20than%20the%20price%20you%20got%20from%20your%20supplier.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20defines%20dropshipping%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20fulfillment%20model%20that%20allows%20entrepreneurs%20to%20outsource%20handling%20and%20shipping%20products%20to%20a%20third%20party.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20walk%20through%20an%20imagined%20example%20of%20the%20process.%20Say%20you%20set%20up%20a%20website%20that%20sells%20handbags%2C%20but%20you%20aren't%20planning%20on%20actually%20keeping%20pallets%20laden%20with%20bags%20in%20your%20garage%20or%20bedroom.%20Instead%2C%20your%20online%20store%20%E2%80%94%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-a-passive-income-on-amazon-fba-2023-8%5C%22%3EAmazon%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20page%2C%20in%20this%20case%20%E2%80%94%20is%20where%20customers%20browse%20and%20place%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20an%20order%20for%20a%20handbag%20is%20placed%2C%20you%20send%20along%20the%20order%20information%20and%20payment%20to%20the%20dropshipper%2C%20and%20that%20entity%20(an%20approved%20dropshipper%2C%20not%20Amazon%20itself)%20handles%20the%20fulfillment.%20Fulfillment%20is%20the%20process%20of%20getting%20the%20bag%20out%20of%20inventory%2C%20packaging%20it%2C%20and%20physically%20shipping%20it%20off%20to%20the%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20dropshipping%2C%20your%20business%20is%20the%20forward-facing%20party%20that%20customers%20see%2C%20while%20a%20third%20party%20handles%20the%20physical%20logistics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20you%20make%20money%20by%20dropshipping%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20profit%20from%20dropshipping%20by%20setting%20a%20higher%20price%20for%20products%20than%20the%20price%20you%20negotiate%20for%20those%20goods%20with%20your%20supplier.%20On%20your%20Amazon%20storefront%20page%2C%20you%20might%20charge%20%2425%20for%20a%20handbag%20you%20can%20buy%20from%20your%20supplier%20for%20%2415.%20The%20margins%20are%20yours%20to%20set%3B%20you%20know%20what%20you'll%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20goods%20on%20the%20backend%20and%20can%20figure%20out%20how%20much%20customers%20are%20willing%20to%20spend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20dropshipping%20still%20allowed%20on%20Amazon%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20dropshipping%20with%20Amazon%20is%20allowed%20and%20legal%2C%20but%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20rules%20you%20need%20to%20follow.%20For%20example%2C%20you%20must%20make%20it%20clear%20on%20all%20customer-facing%20materials%20that%20you%20are%20the%20seller%20of%20record%2C%20so%20any%20shipping%20labels%2C%20packing%20slips%2C%20and%20receipts%20must%20list%20your%20business%2C%20not%20Amazon%20or%20the%20dropshipping%20partner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20you%20are%20responsible%20for%20all%20aspects%20of%20customer%20service%3A%20Amazon's%20mighty%20presence%20and%20powerful%20algorithms%20can%20help%20deliver%20people%20to%20your%20online%20storefront%2C%20but%20it's%20on%20you%20to%20generate%20copy%2C%20note%20sales%20and%20forward%20orders%20along%20to%20your%20shipper%2C%20and%20handle%20any%20issues%20with%20delivery%2C%20product%20quality%2C%20and%20customer%20complaints.%20Amazon%20is%20just%20the%20conduit%2C%20and%20your%20dropshipper%20is%20just%2C%20well%2C%20the%20shipper%20%E2%80%94%20the%20rest%20is%20on%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20much%20does%20it%20cost%20to%20start%20dropshipping%20at%20Amazon%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20Amazon-approved%20dropship%20suppliers%20charge%20onboarding%20fees%3B%20some%20have%20annual%20membership%20costs.%20And%20some%20charge%20a%20small%20fee%20for%20every%20sale%2C%20so%20the%20costs%20vary%20widely.%20Some%20dropshippers%20cost%20nearly%20%24300%20to%20sign%20up%20with%2C%20and%20some%20are%20free.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20you%20will%20need%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-ecommerce-how-to-pick-a-product-to-sell-2023-7%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Seller%3C%2Fa%3E%20account%20to%20dropship%20with%20Amazon%2C%20and%20those%20either%20cost%20%2439.99%20per%20month%20for%20the%20Professional%20Plan%20or%2099%20cents%20per%20item%20sold%20for%20the%20Individual%20Plan.%20You%20can%20upgrade%20(or%20downgrade)%20later%2C%20of%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20dropship%20on%20Amazon%20without%20money%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20best%20things%20about%20dropshipping%20with%20Amazon%20is%20that%20you%20can%20start%20doing%20it%20with%20little%20overhead.%20The%20cost%20of%20the%20seller%20account%20with%20Amazon%20may%20be%20your%20only%20initial%20expense%20if%20you%20find%20a%20dropshipping%20partner%20that%20does%20not%20charge%20a%20fee.%20If%20you%20plan%20to%20grow%20your%20Amazon%20business%20into%20a%20sizeable%20enterprise%2C%20you%20may%20want%20to%20incorporate%20as%20an%20LLC%20to%20shield%20yourself%20from%20legal%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20dropshipping%20suppliers%20work%20with%20Amazon%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERemember%2C%20Amazon%20itself%20is%20not%20the%20dropshipper.%C2%A0%20There%20is%20a%20different%20model%2C%20the%20Amazon%20Affiliate%20model%2C%20wherein%20your%20links%20on%20a%20website%20or%20social%20media%20platform%20send%20customers%20right%20to%20Amazon%2C%20and%20you%20get%20a%20cut%20of%20subsequent%20sales.%20Here%2C%20Amazon%20connects%20you%20to%20customers%20and%20then%20steps%20back.%20When%20you%20get%20an%20order%20paid%20for%2C%20you%20buy%20the%20item%20from%20your%20supplier%20and%20have%20them%20ship%20it%20to%20your%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20Amazon%20dropshipping%20suppliers%20right%20now%20include%20Wholesale2B%2C%20Inventory%20Source%2C%20Banggood%2C%20and%20CJ%20Dropshipping%2C%20to%20name%20just%20a%20few%20%E2%80%94%20a%20quick%20search%20easily%20turns%20up%20many%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20Amazon%20dropshippers%20make%20money%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20indeed%20make%20money%20dropshipping%20via%20Amazon%2C%20and%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20you%20can%20make%20many%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20every%20month.%20But%20take%20note%3A%20the%20average%20profit%20margin%20for%20dropshippers%20is%2015%25.%20At%20the%20lower%20end%2C%20you%20might%20make%20eight%20percent%2C%20and%20at%20the%20highest%2C%2030%25%2C%20according%20to%20BeProfit%2C%20but%20let's%20look%20at%20that%2015%25.%20At%20that%20rate%2C%20if%20your%20handbags%20sell%20for%20%2425%2C%20after%20all%20your%20expenses%2C%20you'd%20make%20%243.75%20for%20each%20sale.%20That%20means%20you'd%20need%20to%20sell%20267%20bags%20before%20you'd%20break%20the%20%241%2C000%20threshold%20in%20profits.%20It's%20doable%2C%20but%20it%20can%20be%20a%20slog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20I%20have%20to%20buy%20inventory%20for%20Amazon%20dropshipping%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20thing%20about%20dropshipping%20is%20arguably%20the%20limited%20startup%20cost%20and%20minimal%20ongoing%20investment%20of%20capital%20needed%2C%20but%20a%20close%20second%20is%20the%20fact%20that%2C%20in