owli%2C%20a%20neighbourhood%20of%20Hyderabad%E2%80%99s%20Old%20City%2C%20after%20disagreements%20arose%20between%20two%20communities%20over%20the%20removal%20of%20religious%20buntings%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFragmentation%20may%20benefit%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWhat%20worries%20a%20section%20of%20Muslims%20is%20the%20fragmentation%20of%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20vote.%20This%20vote%2C%20split%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BRS%2C%20could%20potentially%20be%20devastating.%20An%20office%20bearer%20of%20an%20influential%20socio-religious%20organisation%20who%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20be%20identified%20said%20that%20while%20the%20Congress%20may%20be%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cslightly%20better%E2%80%9D%20position%20in%20Telangana%20given%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20win%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20a%20feeling%20of%20anti-incumbency%20against%20the%20BRS%2C%20there%20was%20no%20Congress%20wave.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20in%20Telangana%20is%20an%20unproven%20entity%2C%20and%20appears%20weak%20at%20the%20grassroots%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9COn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20BRS%20may%20be%20facing%20anti-incumbency%2C%20but%20the%20party%20is%20strong%20at%20the%20grassroots.%20If%20the%20Muslim%20vote%20is%20divided%20between%20the%20BRS%20and%20Congress%2C%20it%20would%20lead%20to%20problems%20in%20constituencies%20in%20the%20composite%20Nizamabad%2C%20and%20Adilabad%20districts%2C%20where%20their%20vote%20is%20important%2C%20and%20benefit%20the%20BJP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWhile%20there%20may%20be%20an%20impression%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20weakened%2C%20this%20is%20likely%20not%20the%20case%2C%20the%20analyst%20said.%20The%20BJP%20vote%20bank%20will%20continue%20to%20hold%20its%20own.%20%E2%80%9CG.%20Kishan%20Reddy%20is%20the%20new%20BJP%20president%2C%20but%20(former%20BJP%20president)%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20continues%20to%20enjoy%20popularity%2C%20especially%20among%20the%20youth.%20The%20party%20is%20likely%20to%20add%20a%20few%20more%20seats%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EProfessor%20Afroz%20Alam%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20Department%20of%20Political%20Science%20at%20the%20Maulana%20Azad%20National%20Urdu%20University%20and%20has%20been%20studying%20the%20election%20climate%20with%20his%20team%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20versus%20BRS%20narrative%20in%20Telangana%20is%20largely%20class-based.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20clear%20divide.%20Elite%20Muslims%20are%20tilting%20towards%20the%20Congress.%20Among%20rural%20Muslims%20who%20are%20beneficiaries%20of%20government%20schemes%2C%20there%20is%20a%20preference%20for%20KCR%2C%E2%80%9D%20Alam%20said.%20He%20opined%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20and%20the%20recent%20win%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Karnataka%20have%20had%20a%20bearing%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Celites%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20little%20or%20no%20anti-incumbency%20against%20BRS%2C%20but%20there%20is%20discontent%20with%20some%20MLAs.%20In%20Karnataka%2C%20everybody%20wanted%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%20In%20Telangana%2C%20that%20situation%20does%20not%20apply%2C%E2%80%9D%20Alam%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697700620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F02134601%2FUntitled-design-2022-06-02T134549.709.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-muslim-voters-dilemma-congress-brs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20is%20appreciated%20for%20maintaining%20communal%20amity%2C%20there%20is%20also%20some%20disappointment%20that%20his%20government%20could%20not%20deliver%20on%20the%20promise%20of%20reservations%20for%20the%20minority%20community.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-muslim-voters-dilemma-congress-brs%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20deets%20on%20Dream%20Girl%202%20OTT%20release%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697700611000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104548473%2Cimgsize-35064.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fdream-girl-2-set-to-drop-on-ott-heres-when-and-how-to-watch-the-ayushmann-khurrana-ananya-panday-starrer%2Farticleshow%2F104548147.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104548147.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAlmost%20two%20months%20after%20its%20release%2C%20the%20movie%20is%20all%20set%20to%20drop%20on%20OTT%20tomorrow%2C%20October%2020%2C%20on%20a%20leading%20OTT%20channel%20and%20can%20be%20watched%20from%20the%20comfort%20of%20your%20home.%20Earlier%2C%20talking%20about%20the%20movie%2C%20Ayushmann%20had%20shared%20that%20the%20movie%20is%20full%20on%20paisa%20vasool%20entertainment.%20He%20told%20a%20media%20outlet%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20slapstick%20film%2C%20a%20frontbencher%2C%20massy%20film.%20We%20are%20not%20really%20touching%20on%20any%20issue%20here.%20It's%20a%20movie%20where%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20take%20your%20brains%20to%20the%20cinema.%20It's%20not%20a%20woke%20film.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fdream-girl-2-set-to-drop-on-ott-heres-when-and-how-to-watch-the-ayushmann-khurrana-ananya-panday-starrer%2Farticleshow%2F104548147.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani%20Commissions%20Largest%20Inter-Regional%20765%20KV%20Transmission%20line%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAdani%20Energy%20Solutions%20Limited%20has%20fully%20commissioned%20the%20Warora%20Kurnool%20Transmission%20line%2C%20spanning%201%2C756%20circuit%20kilometres%20across%20Maharashtra%2C%20Telangana%2C%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20The%20project%20will%20strengthen%20the%20national%20grid%20and%20ensure%20seamless%20flow%20of%204%2C500%20MW%20of%20power%20between%20the%20western%20region%20and%20southern%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20strengthen%20the%20southern%20region%20grid%20and%20support%20large-scale%20integration%20of%20generation%20from%20renewable%20energy%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWarora%20Kurnool%20Transmission%20Limited%20(WKTL)%20was%20incorporated%20in%20April%202015%20to%20establish%20an%20additional%20inter-regional%20alternate%20current%20link%20for%20import%20into%20the%20southern%20region%20-%20%C2%A0Warora-Warangal%20and%20Chilakaluripeta-Hyderabad-Kurnool%20-%20along%20with%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20765%2F400%20kV%20sub-station%20in%20Warangal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWKTL%20is%20the%20largest%20765%20kV%20D%2FC%20(hexa%20conductor)%20tariff-based%20competitive%20bidding%20project%20ever%20awarded%20under%20a%20single%20scheme.%20It%20involved%20the%20laying%20of%20a%201%2C756%20circuit%20kilometre%20(ckm)%20transmission%20line%20traversing%20Maharashtra%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20765%20KV%20sub-station%20in%20Warangal%20on%20a%20build%2C%20own%2C%20operate%20and%20maintain%20basis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20was%20awarded%20to%20Essel%20Infraprojects%20Ltd%20in%20early%202016%20and%20acquired%20by%20Adani%20Energy%20Solutions%20Limited%20(AESL)%20in%20March%2C%202021%2C%20following%20the%20stressed%20debt%20restructuring%20undertaken%20by%20lenders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnough%20Steel%20For%2010%20Eiffel%20Towers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20magnitude%20of%20the%20project%20can%20be%20gauged%20from%20the%20fact%20that%201%2C03%2C000%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20steel%20was%20used%20for%20erecting%20the%20towers%20for%20it.%20This%20equals%20the%20amount%20of%20material%20that%20would%20be%20needed%20to%20set%20up%2010%20Eiffel%20Towers.%20A%20total%20of%2030%2C154%20km%20of%20conductor%20was%20used%20for%20the%20transmission%20lines%2C%20%C2%A0which%20is%20comparable%20to%20making%20three%20rounds%20of%20the%20moon.%20The%20conductor%20material%20is%20made%20from%20a%20specialised%20alloy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first-time%20ever%2C%20two%20mid-stream%20towers%20of%20102%20m%20height%20each%2C%20with%20pile%20foundations%2C%20were%20set%20up%20on%20the%20Krishna%20River.%20Planning%20and%20execution%20was%20crucial%20for%20this%2C%20as%20only%20a%20three-month%20working%20window%20-%20when%20the%20water%20level%20in%20the%20river%20is%20low%20-%20was%20available%20during%20the%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20other%20challenges%20were%20the%20erection%20of%20towers%20and%20the%20stringing%20of%20lines%20crossing%20116%20major%20power%20lines%2C%20electrified%20railway%20tracks%20and%20national%20highways.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20also%20braved%20two%20black%20swan%20global%20events%3A%20Covid-19%20and%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war.%20These%20caused%20disruptions%20in%20the%20entire%20commodity%20supply%20chain%20and%20led%20to%20repeated%20demobilisation%20and%20mobilisation%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20accomplishments%20included%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3E1%2C524%20ckm%20of%20stringing%20was%20completed%20in%2011%20months%2C%20at%20a%20rate%20of%20140%20ckm%2F%20month%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E100%20MT%20tower%20erected%20per%20day%20with%20average%2015%20gangs%20and%20a%20peak%20mobilisation%20of%2040%20gangs%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EPeak%20mobilisation%20of%202%2C000%20workers%20across%20sites%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPresence%20In%2014%20States%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdani%20Energy%20Solutions%20Limited%2C%20part%20of%20the%20Adani%20portfolio%2C%20is%20a%20multidimensional%20organisation%20with%20a%20presence%20in%20various%20facets%20of%20the%20energy%20domain%2C%20including%20power%20transmission%2C%20distribution%2C%20smart%20metering%2C%20and%20cooling%20solutions.%20AESL%20is%20the%20country's%20largest%20private%20transmission%20company%2C%20with%20a%20presence%20across%2014%20states%20of%20India%20and%20a%20cumulative%20transmission%20network%20of%2020%2C000%20ckm%20and%2053%2C000%20MVA%20transformation%20capacity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20distribution%20business%2C%20AESL%20serves%20more%20than%2012%20million%20consumers%20in%20metropolitan%20Mumbai%20and%20the%20industrial%20hub%20of%20Mundra%20SEZ.%20AESL%20is%20ramping%20up%20its%20smart%20metering%20business%20and%20is%20on%20course%20to%20become%20India's%20leading%20smart%20metering%20integrator.%20With%20its%20integrated%20offering%20through%20the%20expansion%20of%20its%20distribution%20network%20through%20parallel%20licenses%20and%20competitive%20and%20tailored%20retail%20solutions%2C%20including%20a%20significant%20share%20of%20green%20power%2C%20AESL%20is%20revolutionising%20the%20way%20energy%20is%20delivered%20to%20the%20end%20consumer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697700480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fkhrp7ojo_adani-transmission-line_625x300_19_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fadani-commissions-largest-inter-regional-765-kv-transmission-line-4495224%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Adani%20Energy%20Solutions%20Limited%20has%20fully%20commissioned%20the%20Warora%20Kurnool%20Transmission%2C%20spanning%201%2C756%20circuit%20kilometres%20across%20Maharashtra%2C%20Telangana%2C%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fadani-commissions-largest-inter-regional-765-kv-transmission-line-4495224%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fadani-commissions-largest-inter-regional-765-kv-transmission-line-4495224%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fadani-commissions-largest-inter-regional-765-kv-transmission-line-4495224%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MP%3A%20Why%20Congress's%20Three%20Promises%20to%20Tribals%20Could%20Be%20a%20Game%20Changer%20in%2047%20ST%20Reserved%20Seats%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19123530%2FThe-Wire-43-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBhopal%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Congress%20is%20sounding%20reasonably%20confident%20of%20improving%20upon%20its%20tally%20of%2031%20in%20the%2047%20seats%20reserved%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(STs)%20it%20won%20in%20the%202018%20assembly%20election%20out%20of%20a%20total%20of%20230%20seats%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20as%20the%20campaign%20gathers%20momentum%20for%20the%20voting%20slated%20on%20November%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20reserved%20ST%20seats%2C%20tribal%20votes%20are%20decisive%20in%20nearly%2040%20general%20seats%20as%20well.%20This%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20both%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20parties%20are%20working%20hard%20to%20woo%20the%20tribal%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202018%20assembly%20elections%2C%20Congress%20was%20successful%20in%20winning%2031%20tribal%20seats%2C%20while%20BJP%20could%20win%20only%2016%20seats.%20In%202013%2C%20BJP%20had%20won%2031%20tribal%20reserved%20seats%20and%20Congress%2015%2C%20whereas%20in%202008%20BJP%20won%2029%20and%20Congress%2017%20ST%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202003%2C%20tribal%20votes%20played%20an%20important%20role%20in%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20return%20to%20power%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20out%20of%2041%20reserved%20seats%20in%20the%20state%2C%20BJP%20could%20win%2037%20and%20Congress%20only%20two%20seats%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThree%20big%20poll%20promises%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20around%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20confidence%20stems%20from%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20three%20promises%20that%20seek%20to%20empower%20the%20tribals%2C%20who%20account%20for%2021%25%20of%20the%20MP%E2%80%99s%20population.%20One%2C%20implementation%20of%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20in%20the%20districts%20having%20more%20than%2050%25%20tribal%20population%3B%20two%2C%20enactment%20of%20the%20PESA%20(Panchayat%2C%20Extension%20to%20Scheduled%20Areas%20Act%2C%201996)%3B%20and%20three%2C%20hike%20in%20the%20rate%20of%20%3Cem%3Etendu%20patta%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0from%20existing%20Rs%203%2C000%20to%20Rs%204%2C000%20per%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19123906%2FF8oD1roWcAAOHje.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19123906%2FF8oD1roWcAAOHje.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19123906%2FF8oD1roWcAAOHje-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19123906%2FF8oD1roWcAAOHje-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680774%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20Congress%20leaders%20at%20the%20release%20of%20the%20party%20manifesto%20on%20October%2017%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40OfficeOfKNath%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20further%20bolstered%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20confidence%20is%20the%20pervasive%20anger%20in%20the%20tribal%20community%20against%20the%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20government%20for%20the%20perceived%20failure%20to%20ensure%20their%20security%2C%20dignity%2C%20and%20cultural%20mores.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20Congress%20promises%2C%20articulated%20by%20its%20national%20general%20secretary%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20in%20an%20election%20rally%20in%20Mandla%20on%20October%2012%20amid%20cheers%20of%20a%20large%20gathering%20in%20the%20predominantly%20tribal%20district%2C%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20transform%20the%20lot%20of%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20promised%20hike%20in%20the%20rate%20of%20Tendu%20leaf%20plucking%20is%20expected%20to%20benefit%20at%20least%2045%20lakh%20people%20in%20the%20tribal%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Sixth%20Schedule%20vests%20the%20tribal%20region%20with%20substantial%20legal%20powers%20to%20protect%20their%20land%20and%20culture.%20It%20is%20in%20force%20in%20the%20northeast%20states%20such%20as%20Meghalaya%2C%20Manipur%2C%20Tripura%2C%20and%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20six%20districts%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20with%20above%2050%25%20tribal%20population%20including%20Barwani%2C%20Alirajpur%2C%20Jhabua%2C%20Dhar%2C%20Dindori%2C%20and%20Mandla.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%2C%20the%20tribal%20community%20will%20have%20the%20right%20to%20make%20and%20implement%20their%20own%20laws%2C%20not%20only%20on%20water%2C%20forests%2C%20and%20land%20but%20also%20on%20marriage%20and%20inheritance%20according%20to%20their%20customs.%20Also%2C%20the%20community%20will%20have%20the%20power%20to%20decide%20who%20will%20have%20mining%20and%20sand%20leases.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20PESA%20act%20will%20empower%20the%20tribal%20regions%20to%20hold%20their%20own%20village%20conference%20(Gram%20Sabhas)%20and%20make%20administrative%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20had%20announced%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Act%20in%20November%20last%20year%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20tribal%20leader%20Birsa%20Munda%2C%20it%20did%20not%20come%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmadhya-pradesh-burhanpur-tribal-forest-rights%5C%22%3EIn%20MP%2C%20Tribal%20Villagers%20Pay%20a%20Heavy%20Price%20for%20Demanding%20Forest%20Rights%2C%20Protesting%20Tree%20Felling%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20law%20empowers%20Gram%20Sabhas%20to%20administer%20the%20areas%20covered%20under%20the%20Fifth%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20under%20which%20the%20rights%20of%20local%20tribes%20over%20water%2C%20forests%2C%20and%20land%2C%20and%20the%20protection%20of%20culture%20are%20ensured.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETribal%20demography%20in%20MP%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2046%20recognised%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20across%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%2052%20districts.%20Of%20these%2C%20six%20major%20tribal%20groups%20%E2%80%93%20Bhil%2C%20Gond%2C%20Kol%2C%20Kurku%2C%20Sahariya%2C%20and%20Baiga%20%E2%80%93%20account%20for%20more%20than%2090%25%20of%20the%201.53%20crore%20tribal%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%2052%20districts%20in%20MP%2C%20six%20are%20predominantly%20inhabited%20by%20tribals%2C%20and%2015%20have%20a%20significant%20tribal%20population.%20The%20Bhil%20community%20constitutes%20the%20largest%20share%2C%20comprising%20about%2040%25%20of%20the%20ST%20population%20in%20the%20state%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20Gonds%20at%2034%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Shivraj%20government%20also%20implemented%20the%20Fifth%20Schedule%20in%2089%20tribal-dominated%20blocks%20of%20the%20state.%20These%20are%20the%20same%20areas%20that%20have%20been%20the%20stronghold%20of%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20has%20promised%20to%20go%20one%20step%20further%20and%20implement%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmp-despite-their-electoral-clout-atrocities-against-tribal-communities-are-on-the-rise%5C%22%3EMP%3A%20Despite%20Their%20Electoral%20Clout%2C%20Atrocities%20Against%20Tribal%20Communities%20Are%20on%20the%20Rise%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECautious%20timing%20of%20the%20announcement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20the%20Congress%20patiently%20waited%20till%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20kicked%20in%20to%20get%20its%20star%20campaigner%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20to%20announce%20the%20three%20promises%20in%20Mandla%2C%20lest%20the%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20government%20might%20steal%20them%20and%20immediately%20implement%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20election%20schedule%20was%20notified%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20had%20managed%20to%20appropriate%20six%20out%20of%2011%20pre-poll%20promises%20to%20the%20farmers%20and%20women%20made%20by%20Congress%20because%20the%20state%20government%20was%20vested%20with%20the%20power%20to%20do%20so.%20Now%2C%20at%20best%2C%20the%20BJP%20can%20incorporate%20similar%20or%20more%20lucrative%20promises%20to%20the%20tribals%20in%20its%20manifesto%2C%20and%20in%20doing%20so%2C%20expose%20itself%20to%20the%20allegation%20of%20being%20a%20copycat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETribal-centric%20campaign%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20electoral%20significance%20of%20the%20place%20where%20Priyanka%20made%20the%20potential%20%E2%80%9Cgame%20changer%E2%80%9D%20promises%20is%20not%20lost%20on%20anyone.%20Mandla%20in%20Mahakoshal%20region%20is%20one%20of%20the%20predominantly%20tribal%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPriyanka%20Gandhi%20has%20so%20far%20held%20four%20public%20meetings%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20out%20of%20which%20three%20have%20been%20held%20in%20tribal-dominated%20areas.%20She%20started%20her%20election%20campaign%20in%20the%20state%20from%20Jabalpur%20in%20Mahakaushal%2C%20which%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20tribal-dominated.%20Then%2C%20she%20addressed%20rallies%20in%20Dhar%20district%20in%20Malwa%20and%20Mandla%20in%20the%20Mahakosal%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20all%20the%20rallies%20she%20emphasised%20that%20the%20thinking%20of%20Congress%20has%20been%20to%20increase%20the%20respect%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20traditions%20of%20the%20tribals%20and%20that%20was%20why%20the%20Forest%20Rights%20Act%20was%20enacted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDifference%20in%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20approaches%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20is%20unsparing%20in%20its%20efforts%20to%20further%20broad-base%20its%20sway%20on%20the%20tribal%20belts%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20too%2C%20is%20fiercely%20competing%20with%20its%20rival%20to%20regain%20the%20lost%20trust%20of%20the%20community%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20fundamental%20difference%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20in%20their%20approach%20towards%20tribals%20is%20discernible.%20The%20BJP%20appears%20condescending%20towards%20the%20community%20whereas%20the%20Congress%20is%20focused%20on%20their%20empowerment.%20The%20BJP%20tends%20to%20see%20and%20call%20the%20tribals%20%E2%80%9CVanvasi%E2%80%9D%20(forest%20dwellers)%2C%20the%20Congress%20acknowledges%20them%20as%20Adivasi%20(original%20inhabitants).%20The%20difference%20in%20nomenclature%20is%20just%20not%20semantic%20quibbling.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20rally%20in%20poll-bound%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Shahdol%20district%20on%20October%2011%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20criticised%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98Vanvasi%E2%80%99%20to%20refer%20to%20the%20tribal%20community%20and%20claimed%20he%20forced%20the%20PM%20to%20use%20the%20word%20Adivasi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20difference%20between%20the%20words%20Adivasi%20and%20Vanvasi.%20Adivasi%20means%20those%20who%20came%20to%20Hindustan%20first%20and%20who%20are%20owners%20of%20this%20land%20while%20Vanvasis%20are%20those%20living%20in%20the%20forest%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rahul%20said%20at%20the%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20listen%20to%20Narendra%20Modi%20Ji%E2%80%99s%20speech%20%E2%80%93%20he%20no%20longer%20says%20Vanvasi%2C%20he%20says%20Adivasi.%20Adivasi%20is%20the%20word%20that%20comes%20out%20of%20the%20mouth%2C%20but%20Vanvasi%20is%20in%20the%20heart%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Vanvasi%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20means%20forest%20dwellers%2C%20is%20a%20term%20used%20by%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20ideological%20parent%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%2C%20which%20works%20extensively%20in%20tribal%20areas%2C%20and%20claims%20%E2%80%9Cto%20protect%20them%20from%20the%20clutches%20of%20Christian%20missionaries%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETribal%20leadership%20crisis%20in%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20glaring%20difference%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20vis-a-vis%20the%20tribals%20is%20visible%20in%20leadership.%20The%20Congress%20has%20appointed%20former%20Union%20minister%20Kantilal%20Bhuria%20as%20the%20head%20of%20its%20state%20election%20campaign%20committee.%20The%2073-year-old%20Congress%20leader%20belongs%20to%20the%20Bhil%20tribe%2C%20the%20largest%20tribe%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20from%202004-2011.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20relegated%20its%20only%20important%20tribal%20leader%20and%20Union%20minister%20Faggan%20Singh%20Kulaste%20to%20fight%20in%20the%20Niwas%20seat%20in%20the%20Mandla%20district%20where%20the%20Congress%20had%20won%20by%20a%20margin%20of%20over%2028%2C000%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20many%20prominent%20tribal%20faces%20in%20the%20second%20line%20of%20leadership%20such%20as%20Umang%20Singhar%20and%20Bala%20Bachchan.%20The%20BJP%20sorely%20lacks%20a%20second%20line%20of%20tribal%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETribal%20welfare%20or%20event%20management%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOwing%20to%20the%20glaring%20absence%20of%20powerful%20tribal%20voices%20within%20the%20BJP%20that%20would%20alert%20the%20state%20government%20to%20the%20real%20concerns%20of%20the%20community%2C%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20virtually%20reduced%20the%20tribal%20welfare%20to%20event%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20empowering%20the%20tribals%20in%20the%20true%20sense%20with%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20PESA%20and%20the%20Fifth%20Schedule%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20has%20held%20extravagant%20tribal%20congregations%20across%20the%20state%20where%20he%20entertained%20the%20government-sponsored%20crowds%20with%20the%20announcements%20of%20emotion-filled%20tokenism%20such%20as%20naming%20a%20railway%20station%20after%20one%20tribal%20hero%20here%20and%20setting%20up%20a%20museum%20in%20the%20name%20of%20another%20tribal%20hero%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAllowing%20tribals%20to%20brew%20their%20own%20Mahua%20and%20selling%20the%20product%20from%20government%20outlets%20as%20an%20exotic%20brand%20name%20has%20been%20widely%20publicised%20as%20the%20Shivraj%20government%E2%80%99s%20great%20achievement.%20Distribution%20of%20free%20ration%20in%20the%2089%20tribal%20blocks%20has%20been%20passed%20off%20as%20another%20big%20feat%20of%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETribal%20outreach%20began%20in%202021%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20management%20series%20to%20woo%20the%20tribals%20was%20launched%20in%20a%20big%20way%20in%20September%202021in%20Jabalpur%20with%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20participating%20in%20a%20function%20to%20mark%20the%20martyrdom%20of%20tribal%20king%20Shankar%20Shah%20and%20his%20son%20Raghunath%20Shah.%20The%20tribal%20royals%20were%20blown%20off%20with%20their%20bodies%20tied%20to%20a%20cannon%20by%20the%20British%20for%20their%20involvement%20in%20the%201857%20mutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Jabalpur%20conclave%20was%20followed%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20rechristening%20Bhopal%E2%80%99s%20Habibganj%20railway%20station%20after%20the%20name%20of%20Gond%20queen%20Rani%20Kamalapati%20on%20November%2015%2C%202021%20in%20Bhopal.%20%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20a%20slew%20of%20tribal%20gatherings%20followed%20in%20various%20tribal%20regions%20across%20the%20state%20which%20witnessed%20chief%20minister%20Chouhan%20announcing%20a%20plethora%20of%20welfare%20schemes%20for%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20are%20tribals%20aggrieved%3F%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20these%20announcements%20have%20been%20more%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20tokenism%20and%20have%20failed%20to%20address%20the%20real%20worries%20of%20the%20tribals.%20They%20expected%20the%20government%20to%20ensure%20their%20security%20with%20dignity%2C%20without%20them%20having%20to%20jettison%20their%20culture%20and%20deities.%20The%20government%20has%20let%20them%20down%20on%20these%20counts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFar%20from%20seeing%20the%20government%20as%20their%20saviour%2C%20the%20tribal%20community%20in%20the%20state%20has%20come%20to%20regard%20it%20as%20a%20collaborator%20of%20the%20upper%20caste%20exploiters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13084854%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-12-at-11.17.37-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13084854%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-12-at-11.17.37-AM.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13084854%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-12-at-11.17.37-AM-300x224.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662941%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22766%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20April%202023%20protest%20by%20Burhanpur%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20villagers.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%2020%20years%2C%20numerous%20cases%20have%20come%20to%20light%20where%20powerful%20people%2C%20aligned%20with%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20forcibly%20grabbed%20tribals%E2%80%99%20land.%20In%20one%20such%20case%2C%20veteran%20Congress%20leader%20Digvijay%20Singh%20accused%20the%20state%20BJP%20president%20V.D.%20Sharma%20of%20protecting%20a%20land-grabber%20in%20the%20Panna%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnger%20erupts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETribals%20have%20in%20most%20cases%20endured%20atrocities%20against%20them%20with%20helplessness%20but%20there%20have%20been%20occasions%20when%20their%20pent-up%20anger%20erupted%2C%20causing%20embarrassment%20to%20the%20government.%20The%20latest%20in%20a%20series%20of%20the%20cases%20of%20brutality%20against%20tribals%20came%20to%20the%20fore%20in%20July%20this%20year%20when%20a%20video%20went%20viral%20showing%20a%20BJP%20worker%20urinating%20on%20a%20tribal.%20This%20incident%20caused%20a%20major%20furore%20in%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20viral%20video%20outraged%20the%20nation%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20called%20the%20victim%20of%20the%20despicable%20crime%20to%20his%20bungalow%20in%20Bhopal%20and%20dramatically%20washed%20his%20feet.%20From%20publicly%20apologising%20to%20the%20poor%20tribal%20and%20granting%20him%20financial%20aid%2C%20to%20razing%20the%20house%20of%20accused%20Pravesh%20Shukla%20and%20charging%20him%20under%20the%20National%20Security%20Act%20(NSA)%2C%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20acted%20swiftly%20to%20contain%20the%20potential%20damage%20from%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F07205047%2FF0VC_s3aIAA3CbI.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F07205047%2FF0VC_s3aIAA3CbI.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F07205047%2FF0VC_s3aIAA3CbI-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662205%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20washes%20the%20feet%20of%20Dashmat%20Rawat%2C%20the%20urination%20case%20victim%2C%20at%20CM%20House%2C%20in%20Bhopal.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40ChouhanShivraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EPravesh%20Shukla%20was%20a%20representative%20of%20the%20BJP%20MLA%20from%20Siddhi%2C%20Kedarnath%20Shukla.%20The%20MLA%20has%20been%20denied%20a%20ticket%20by%20the%20BJP.%20He%20has%20announced%20to%20contest%20as%20an%20independent%20against%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20candidate%20and%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20Riti%20Pathak.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20move%20is%20unlikely%20to%20prompt%20the%20tribals%20to%20forgive%20and%20forget%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%20indignity%20one%20of%20their%20men%20underwent.%20For%2C%20atrocities%20against%20India%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20people%20are%20not%20new%2C%20especially%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwatch-mp-man-seen-urinating-on-tribal-youth-arrested-allegations-of-bjp-links%5C%22%3EWatch%20%7C%20MP%20Man%20Seen%20Urinating%20on%20Tribal%20Youth%20Arrested%2C%20Allegations%20of%20BJP%20Links%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECases%20of%20brutalities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20July%202%2C%202022%2C%20the%20internet%20was%20flooded%20with%20visuals%20of%20the%20public%20immolation%20of%20a%20tribal%20woman%2C%20Rampyari%20Bai%2C%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Guna%20district.%20Her%20family%20lives%20in%20Dhanoria%20village%20and%20belong%20to%20the%20Sahariya%20tribe.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20year%20earlier%2C%20in%20an%20incident%20in%20Dewas%20district%2C%20one%20Surendra%20Chauhan%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20his%20aides%2C%20killed%20five%20members%20of%20an%20Adivasi%20family%20over%20his%20relationship%20with%20an%20Adivasi%20woman%20that%20went%20wrong%20and%20buried%20their%20bodies%20in%20an%20eight-feet-deep%20pit.%20The%20bodies%20were%20found%20only%20after%2045%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202021%2C%20Kanhaiya%20Lal%20Bheel%20was%20beaten%2C%20tied%20up%2C%20and%20then%20dragged%20by%20a%20truck%20on%20a%20tarred%20road.%20He%20later%20died%20in%20the%20hospital.%20He%20was%20treated%20worse%20than%20an%20animal%2C%20on%20suspicion%20of%20theft%20in%20Neemuch%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202021%2C%20Sampatlal%20Batti%20and%20Dhansay%20Inwati%2C%20both%20tribal%20people%2C%20were%20beaten%20to%20death%20by%20alleged%20Bajrang%20Dal%20members%20on%20the%20mere%20suspicion%20of%20cow%20slaughter%20in%20Seoni%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHorrifying%20statistics%20of%20crimes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20is%20home%20to%2013.6%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20population%2C%2023.5%25%20of%20crimes%20against%20tribal%20people%20in%20India%20take%20place%20in%20MP.%20Almost%2025%25%20of%20all%20crimes%20against%20tribal%20people%20in%20India%20take%20place%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20report%20%3Cem%3ECrime%20in%20India%202021%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20reported%202%2C627%20cases%20filed%20under%20the%20SC%2FST%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%20in%202021.%20The%20number%20increased%20from%202%2C401%20in%202020%20and%201%2C922%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20NCRB%20also%20reported%20that%20in%20the%20year%202021%20itself%2C%2052%20cases%20of%20murder%20were%20reported%20in%20which%20the%20victims%20were%20Adivasi%20persons.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20category%20of%20assault%20on%20tribal%20women%20with%20the%20intent%20to%20outrage%20their%20modesty%2C%20308%20cases%20were%20reported%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20NCRB%20also%20reported%20376%20cases%20of%20rape%20against%20Adivasi%20women%20in%20the%20state%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20numbers%2C%20however%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20capture%20the%20pervasive%20violence%20the%20Adivasis%2C%20especially%20the%20ones%20who%20live%20inside%20or%20near%20forest%20areas%2C%20have%20to%20face%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20state%20agents%20such%20as%20forest%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnresponsive%20BJP%20to%20their%20woes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20dismal%20backdrop%20of%20the%20tribals%E2%80%99%20plight%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20are%20fiercely%20competing%20to%20garner%20their%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%205%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20in%20tribal-dominated%20Jabalpur%20where%20he%20laid%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20Gond%20warrior%20queen%20Rani%20Durgavati%E2%80%99s%20memorial.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20same%20day%2C%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20was%20in%20another%20ST-dominated%20district%2C%20Dhar%2C%20where%20she%20unveiled%20the%20statue%20of%20tribal%20hero%20Tantya%20Mama%2C%20a%20Bhil%20revolutionary%20who%20fought%20the%20British.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20his%20remarks%20at%20the%20election%20rally%20attacked%20the%20Congress%20but%20did%20not%20say%20a%20word%20about%20the%20condition%20of%20tribals%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20much%20less%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20steps%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20in%20September%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20flagged%20off%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20third%20Jan%20Ashirwad%20Yatra%20in%20the%20predominantly%20tribal%20Mandla%20district%2C%20saying%20that%20while%20Congress%20was%20focused%20on%20minority%20appeasement%2C%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20working%20for%20tribals%2C%20Dalits%2C%20and%20the%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20dwelt%20at%20length%20on%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20decisions%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20tribals%20but%20did%20not%20mention%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20performance%20towards%20the%20tribals.%20He%20only%20reminded%20that%20the%20BJP-led%20Centre%20has%20set%20up%20museums%20on%20Birsa%20Munda%2C%20Shankar%20Shah%2C%20Raghunath%20Shah%2C%20Rani%20Durgavati%2C%20and%20other%20tribal%20freedom%20fighters%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShivraj%E2%80%99s%20government%20achievements%20are%20conspicuously%20absent%20in%20the%20top%20BJP%20leaders%E2%80%99%20speeches.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20days%20(PM)%20Modi%20feels%20shy%20of%20even%20taking%20Shivraj%E2%80%99s%20name.%20He%20has%20started%20saying%20vote%20for%20me.%20Shivraj%20is%20not%20going%20to%20become%20your%20CM%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20remarked%20in%20the%20Dhar%20election%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202023%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20started%20a%20tribal%20outreach%20campaign%20from%20Balaghat%20to%20attract%20tribal%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBSP-GGP%20alliance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmid%20competition%20between%20the%20two%20main%20rivals%2C%20an%20alliance%20between%20the%20predominantly%20Dalit%20party%20BSP%20and%20tribal-centric%20GGP%20has%20given%20an%20interesting%20twist%20to%20the%20electoral%20politics%20around%20tribals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20and%20the%20Gondwana%20Gantantra%20Party%20(GGP)%20have%20formed%20an%20alliance%20for%20the%20first%20time%20ever%20to%20contest%20the%20polls%20in%20a%20state%2C%20which%20has%20traditionally%20been%20dominated%20by%20two%20parties%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20their%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%20for%20the%20elections%20to%20the%20230-member%20MP%20Assembly%2C%20the%20BSP%20will%20contest%20178%20constituencies%20while%20the%20GGP%20will%20field%20its%20candidates%20in%2052%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFormed%20in%201991%2C%20the%20GGP%20is%20concentrated%20in%20the%20Gondi%20people%2C%20a%20major%20tribal%20group%20in%20MP%2C%20championing%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20state%20of%20Gondwana%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20GGP%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20vote%20base%20is%20located%20in%20the%20Mahakaushal%20region%2C%20mainly%20in%20the%20districts%20of%20Balaghat%2C%20Mandla%2C%20Dindori%2C%20Seoni%2C%20Chhindwara%2C%20and%20Betul%2C%20which%20have%20a%20notable%20Gondi%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDalits%20make%20up%20about%2016%25%20of%20MP%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20with%2035%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20total%20230%20Assembly%20seats%20reserved%20for%20the%20SCs.%20In%20the%202018%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%2018%20of%20these%20seats%2C%20with%2017%20going%20to%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20GGP%20had%20fielded%2061%20candidates%20in%20the%202003%20state%20polls%2C%20of%20whom%20three%20were%20elected.%20However%2C%20it%20has%20since%20failed%20to%20win%20any%20seat%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%20as%20the%20party%20has%20been%20beset%20by%20factionalism%20and%20infighting.%20It%20had%20formed%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20in%20the%202018%20polls%2C%20in%20which%20the%20SP%20managed%20to%20win%20one%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20GGP-BSP%20alliance%20is%20unlikely%20to%20significantly%20impact%20the%20voting%20outcome%2C%20according%20to%20opinion%20polls%20that%20hav