osing%20arguments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichel%2C%20a%20founding%20member%20of%20the%20Grammy-winning%20hip-hop%20group%20Fugees%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fopa%2Fpr%2Fus-entertainer-convicted-engaging-foreign-influence-campaign%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewas%20convicted%20in%20April%20of%2010%20federal%20charges%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20conspiring%20to%20make%20and%20conceal%20foreign%20campaign%20contributions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20trying%20to%20persuade%20US%20officials%20to%20drop%20an%20investigation%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ffugitive-financier-jho-low-denies-being-mastermind-behind-1mdb-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJho%20Low%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Malaysian%20financier%20accused%20of%20playing%20a%20central%20role%20in%20a%20massive%20%244.5%20billion%20fraud%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Kenner%2C%20an%20attorney%20known%20for%20representing%20Suge%20Knight%2C%20Tupac%20Shakur%2C%20and%20Snoop%20Dogg%2C%20ran%20Michel's%20defense%20for%20the%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Michel's%20new%20lawyers%2C%20a%20legal%20team%20from%20ArentFox%20Schiff%2C%20now%20say%20Kenner%20botched%20the%20defense%20by%20using%20an%20%26quot%3Bexperimental%20artificial%20intelligence%20program%26quot%3B%20to%20draft%20his%20closing%20arguments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Monday%20filing%20seen%20by%20Insider%2C%20Michel's%20lawyers%20alleged%20that%20Kenner%20used%20a%20program%20called%20EyeLevel.AI%2C%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Bignoring%20the%20best%20arguments%20and%20conflating%20the%20charged%20schemes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMichel%20never%20had%20a%20chance%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ArentFox%20Schiff%20team%20wrote%2C%20adding%20that%20Michel's%20legal%20defense%20was%20%26quot%3Bdeficient%20throughout.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichel's%20lawyers%20said%20his%20former%20publicist%20told%20them%20about%20Kenner%20using%20EyeLevel.AI%20to%20write%20the%20closing%20arguments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20pointed%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eyelevel.ai%2Fpost%2Ffirst-use-of-ai-in-federal-trial%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMay%2010%20product%20update%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20EyeLevel.AI%2C%20which%20said%20that%20Kenner%20had%20used%20the%20program%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20use%20of%20generative%20AI%20in%20a%20federal%20trial.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20absolute%20game%20changer%20for%20complex%20litigation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20press%20release%20cited%20Kenner%20as%20saying.%20%26quot%3BThe%20system%20turned%20hours%20or%20days%20of%20legal%20work%20into%20seconds.%20This%20is%20a%20look%20into%20the%20future%20of%20how%20cases%20will%20be%20conducted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEyeLevel.AI%20said%20its%20system%20%26quot%3Bhelps%20lawyers%20become%2010x%20faster%20and%20more%20effective.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichel's%20lawyers%20also%20accused%20Kenner%20and%20his%20co-counsel%20of%20holding%20an%20undisclosed%20financial%20stake%20in%20EyeLevel.AI%2C%20and%20alleged%20that%20the%20pair%20used%20the%20program%20for%20Michel's%20defense%20so%20they%20could%20issue%20the%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ArentFox%20Schiff%20team%20alleged%20that%20law%20firms%20for%20Kenner%20and%20his%20co-counsel%20share%20addresses%20with%20CaseFile%20Connect%20%E2%80%94%20a%20technology%20partner%20with%20EyeLevel.AI.%20These%20firms%20are%20located%20in%20Encino%2C%20California%2C%20and%20New%20York%20City%2C%20per%20ArentFox%20Schiff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyers%20said%20this%20%26quot%3Bappears%20to%20confirm%26quot%3B%20that%20Kenner%20had%20a%20financial%20interest%20in%20the%20AI%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEyeLevel.AI%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Insider%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20told%20several%20outlets%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20Kenner%20and%20his%20co-counsel%20don't%20have%20any%20stake%20in%20EyeLevel.AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNeither%20Kenner%20Law%20nor%20its%20associates%20have%20a%20financial%20stake%20in%20EyeLevel%20as%20claimed%20in%20the%20filing.%20They%20were%20happy%20with%20our%20AI's%20capabilities%20and%20provided%20a%20quote%20for%20a%20press%20release%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedailybeast.com%2Fdavid-kenner-star-hip-hop-lawyer-accused-of-using-ai-in-big-case-he-lost%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEyeLevel.AI%20told%20The%20Daily%20Beast.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ArentFox%20Schiff%20team%20also%20accused%20Kenner%20of%20providing%20inadequate%20defense%20for%20Michel%2C%20alleging%20that%20he%20wasn't%20well-versed%20in%20white-collar%20crime%20and%20outsourced%20trial%20preparations%20and%20strategy%20to%20contract%20attorneys%20at%20a%20friend's%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20listed%20what%20they%20said%20were%20six%20issues%20in%20Michel's%20defense%2C%20including%20a%20failure%20by%20Kenner%20to%20object%20to%20hearsay%20or%20prejudicial%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKenner%20and%20the%20ArentFox%20Schiff%20team%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichel's%20sentencing%20date%20has%20not%20been%20set%2C%20but%20he%20faces%20up%20to%2020%20years%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpras-michel-lawyer-artificial-intelligence-closing-argument-david-kenner-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697699999000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6530bd94211def8ed838d9d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpras-michel-lawyer-artificial-intelligence-closing-argument-david-kenner-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Michel's%20ex-attorney%2C%20David%20Kenner%2C%20was%20quoted%20in%