39%25%20less%20than%20the%20peak%20in%20Q2%20of%202018-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20marker%20of%20continuing%20distress%2C%20particularly%20in%20rural%20and%20semiurban%20areas%2C%20gold%20loan%20companies%20are%20facing%20a%20surge%20in%20demand%20ahead%20of%20the%20festive%20season%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Fbanking%2Ffinance%2Frush-for-gold-cash-amid-need-for-cold-cash%2Farticleshow%2F104507422.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20A%20gold%20loan%20is%20a%20cash%20loan%20provided%20with%20gold%20being%20the%20collateral.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20one%20explanation%20could%20be%20that%20people%20are%20wanting%20to%20spend%20more%20this%20festive%20season%20as%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20has%20eased%2C%20the%20rush%20for%20loans%20suggests%20their%20incomes%20are%20not%20able%20to%20provide%20enough%20liquidity.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20erratic%20monsoon%20in%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20may%20have%20also%20dented%20rural%20incomes%2C%20forcing%20people%20to%20borrow%20against%20their%20gold%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697697058000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19113729%2Fmohit-tomar-2Dss2gbE9eA-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Flow-small-vehicle-sales-rush-for-gold-loans-point-to-economic-distress%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sales%20of%20both%20small%20cars%20and%20two-wheelers%20are%20at%20their%20lowest%20since%20a%20peak%20in%202018-19.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Flow-small-vehicle-sales-rush-for-gold-loans-point-to-economic-distress%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20court%20extends%20Manish%20Sisodia's%20judicial%20custody%20till%20Nov%2022%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22pu