0and%20is%20not%20in%20the%20long%20term%20American%20interest%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20Administration%E2%80%99s%20response%20%E2%80%93%20and%20much%20of%20Congress%E2%80%99%20as%20well%20%E2%80%93%20is%20an%20impulsive%20reaction%20built%20on%20confirmation%20bias%2C%20political%20convenience%2C%20intellectual%20bankruptcy%2C%20and%20bureaucratic%20inertia.%20That%20is%20to%20say%2C%20it%20is%20immensely%20disappointing%2C%20and%20entirely%20unsurprising.%20Decades%20of%20the%20same%20approach%20have%20shown%20that%20security%20for%20peace%20leads%20to%20neither%20security%2C%20nor%20to%20peace.%20The%20fact%20is%2C%20blind%20support%20for%20one%20side%20is%20destructive%20in%20the%20long%20term%20to%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20people%20on%20both%20sides.%20I%20fear%20we%20are%20repeating%20the%20same%20mistakes%20we%20have%20made%20these%20past%20decades%2C%20and%20I%20decline%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20it%20for%20longer%2C%E2%80%9D%20Paul%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHuffPost%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20other%20State%20Department%20officials%20who%20feel%20similarly%20to%20Paul%20have%20been%20experiencing%20a%20%E2%80%9Cchilling%20effect%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20has%20been%20unequivocally%20backing%20Israel%20during%20the%20last%20week.%20Even%20after%20a%20recent%20strike%20on%20a%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%20killed%20at%20least%20500%20Palestinians%2C%20Biden%20%E2%80%93%20while%20visiting%20Israel%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fisrael-hamas-war-biden-backs-israel-account-on-gaza-blast%2Flive-67128528%5C%22%3Eechoed%20the%20Israeli%20administration%E2%80%99s%20line%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20devastation%20was%20caused%20by%20a%20misfired%20Hamas%20rocket.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697691148000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19101948%2FF8uduyaWoAAr3mW.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthew