mb%20shelter%20near%20the%20Nova%20Festival%20and%20blocked%20at%20least%206%20grenades%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee%2CAlisa%20Shodiyev%20Kaff)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A61%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foff-duty-israeli-soldier-nova-music-festival-blocked-grenades-hamas-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20Malnutrition%20Protocol%20Is%20More%20%E2%80%98Wait%20and%20Watch%E2%80%99%20Than%20Tangible%20Interventions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18165942%2FScreenshot-2023-10-18-at-4.57.27.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20new%20protocol%20for%20management%20of%20malnutrition%20in%20children%20released%20by%20Union%20minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20on%20October%2011%2C%202023%2C%20acknowledges%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Enutrition%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20in%20health%20and%20development%20and%20is%20%E2%80%98one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20challenges%20facing%20contemporary%20India%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20of%20the%20strategies%20presented%20in%20the%20protocol%20seem%20to%20suggest%20a%20wait%20and%20watch%20approach%20till%20after%20malnutrition%20has%20set%20in.%20Unfortunately%2C%20as%20the%20protocol%20itself%20mentions%2C%20malnutrition%20can%20often%20have%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eirreversible%20long%20and%20short-term%20consequences%2C%20even%20with%20interventions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20is%20a%20holistic%20approach%20as%20promised%20by%20the%20Poshan%20Abhiyan%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20protocol%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ementions%20several%20determinants%20of%20undernutrition%20such%20as%20low%20income%2C%20large%20family%20size%2C%20gender%20bias%2C%20changing%20crop%20patterns%2C%20lack%20of%20knowledge%2C%20poor%20health%20etc.%20which%20lead%20to%20dietary%20imbalance%2C%20reduced%20access%20to%20food%2C%20loss%20of%20traditional%20food%20habits%20etc.%20Many%20of%20these%20determinants%20end%20up%20being%20attributed%20to%20communities%20and%20families%2C%20especially%20mothers.%20If%20the%20%E2%80%98holistic%20approach%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20Poshan%20Abhiyan%20is%20to%20be%20realised%20in%20spirit%20and%20practice%20and%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20evidence%20based%20nutrition%2C%20all%20barriers%20to%20good%20nutrition%20%E2%80%93%20economic%2C%20social%2C%20political%2C%20cultural%20and%20religious%20should%20be%20objectively%20documented%20and%20addressed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20protocol%20states%20that%20diet%20diversity%20should%20be%20followed%20when%20constructing%20diets%20for%20malnourished%20children%20and%20it%20is%20good%20that%20nutrient%20dense%20foods%20such%20as%20egg%20and%20whole%20milk%20have%20been%20included.%20Eggs%2C%20which%20contain%20important%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faharanammahakku.home.blog%2F2023%2F02%2F21%2Ffactsheet-1-eggs%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enutrients%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eshould%20ideally%20be%20given%20on%20all%20days%20of%20the%20week%20to%20all%20children%20and%20not%20to%20just%20to%20those%20identified%20with%20malnutrition.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThose%20with%20religious%2C%20caste%20or%20health%20restrictions%20on%20eggs%20should%20be%20given%20an%20additional%20glass%20of%20milk%20or%20a%20bowl%20of%20yoghurt.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20(on%20paper)%2C%20people%20are%20encouraged%20to%20eat%20their%20%E2%80%98traditional%20foods%E2%80%99%2C%20very%20often%20these%20are%20made%20inaccessible%20to%20them%20because%20of%20economic%2C%20political%20or%20social%20reasons.%20Erasing%20and%20criminalising%20animal%20source%20foods%20consumed%20by%20many%20communities%20institutionalises%20caste%20and%20communal%20prejudices.%20This%20is%20very%20evident%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20example%2C%20organisations%20such%20as%20Akshaya%20Patra%2C%20which%20have%20bagged%20mid-day%20meal%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Fpulse%2F905334%2Fno-onion-no-garlic-akshaya-patra-opposes-karnataka-government-order-on-mid-day-meals%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econtract%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Es%20in%20several%20states%20in%20India%2C%20take%20a%20belligerent%2C%20unscientific%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esattvik%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(anti-meat%2C%20anti-egg)%20stance%20which%20is%20a%20serious%20impediment%2C%20often%20intergenerational%2C%20to%20addressing%20malnutrition%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20also%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faharanammahakku.home.blog%2F2021%2F11%2F15%2Freport-the-adverse-impact-of-the-karnataka-prevention-of-slaughter-and-preservation-of-cattle-act-2020%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecattle%20slaughter%20bans%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20economic%20boycotts%20of%20Muslim%20communities%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faharanammahakku.home.blog%2F2022%2F05%2F05%2Ftargeting-the-consumption-and-sale-of-meat-in-india-is-an-attack-on-the-right-to-food-and-nutrition%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebanning%20meat%20shops%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20etc.%20adversely%20affects%20people%E2%80%99s%20access%20to%20nutrient%20dense%20foods%20and%20creates%20shame%20around%20these%20foods.%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98multi-pronged%20strategies%E2%80%99%20of%20criminalising%20and%2For%20erasing%20nutrient%20dense%20foods%20on%20the%20one%20hand%20while%20also%20pretending%20to%20hold%20the%20mantle%20against%20malnutrition%2C%20therefore%20reeks%20of%20dishonesty%20and%20duplicity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPreventing%20rather%20than%20treating%20malnutrition%20should%20be%20the%20primary%20goal%20of%20any%20nutritional%20intervention%20programme.%20Children%20with%20stunting%20and%20undernutrition%20are%20likely%20to%20have%20a%20host%20of%20other%20nutritional%20deficiencies%20which%20make%20them%20susceptible%20to%20anemia%2C%20night%20blindness%2C%20cognitive%20deficiency%2C%20skin%20disease%2C%20respiratory%2C%20gastro-intestinal%20disease%2C%20etc.%20Viewed%20in%20that%20context%2C%20the%20rapid%20push%20for%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fnews%2Frice-fortification-is-the-wrong-fix-for-indias-anaemia-and-malnutrition-problems%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efortification%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20government%20stands%20out%20as%20woefully%20inappropriate%20and%20unholistic.%20In%20a%20country%20with%20alarming%20hunger%20and%20multiple%20nutritional%20deficiencies%2C%20fortifying%20the%20nutrient-poor%20and%20over%20consumed%20cereals%20with%20one%20or%20two%20%E2%80%98micro-nutrients%E2%80%99%20is%20neither%20economic%20nor%20a%20solution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Poshan%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.poshantracker.in%2Ffaq%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etracker%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20focuses%20inordinately%20on%20the%20Aadhaar%20card%20in%20spite%20of%20several%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Faadhaar-right-to-food-pain-exclusion%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econcerns%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20about%20it%2C%20pushing%20those%20most%20in%20need%20of%20social%20security%20to%20fall%20through%20the%20gaps.%20Aadhaar-verified%20beneficiaries%20are%209%2C55%2C73%2C667%20(9.6%20crore)%20out%20of%2010%2C10%2C89%2C751%20(10%20crore)%20eligible%20beneficiaries%2C%20which%20means%20that%20only%2094%25%20are%20verified%20and%2055%2C16%2C084%20(0.55%20lakhs)%20have%20been%20left%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20in%20aspirational%20districts%20and%20in%20the%20northeast%20region%2C%20of%20a%20total%20of%2022%2C71%2C111%20adolescent%20girls%2C%20only%2018%2C71%2C228%20(82%25)%20are%20Aadhaar%20verified.%20Of%20these%203%2C22%2C807%20have%20received%20take%20home%20rations.%20What%20is%20%E2%80%98holistic%E2%80%99%20about%20leaving%20out%20vast%20sections%20of%20people%2C%20especially%20those%20most%20in%20need%20of%20social%20security%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20thus%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20wishful%20desire%20(on%20paper)%20for%20an%20%E2%80%98overarching%20scheme%20for%20holistic%20nourishment%E2%80%99%20through%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fposhanabhiyaan.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPoshan%20Abhiyan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20in%20reality%20it%20is%20neither%20overarching%20nor%20holistic.%20Neither%20is%20it%20adequately%20nourishing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F17123202%2F108201-aeveizlzly-1544899613.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F17123202%2F108201-aeveizlzly-1544899613.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F17123202%2F108201-aeveizlzly-1544899613-300x158.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F17123202%2F108201-aeveizlzly-1544899613-1024x538.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338592%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EChildren%20in%20an%20Odisha%20school%20eat%20their%20midday%20meal.%20Photo%3A%20mdmodisha.nic.in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENo%20appetite%20for%20a%20test%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20protocol%20lays%20emphasis%20on%20the%20appetite%20test%20to%20be%20conducted%20by%20the%20Anganwadi%20worker%20on%20children%20with%20Severe%20Acute%20Malnutrition%20(SAM)%20children%20using%20a%20hot%20cooked%20meal%20from%20the%20Anganwadi.%20Only%20those%20children%20who%20%E2%80%98fail%E2%80%99%20this%20%E2%80%98test%E2%80%99%20will%20be%20referred%20to%20the%20Nutrition%20Rehabilitation%20Centres%20(NRC)%2C%20while%20those%20who%20%E2%80%98pass%E2%80%99%20will%20be%20enrolled%20under%20the%20Supplementary%20Nutrition%20programme%20and%20referred%20to%20the%20primary%20health%20centre%20medical%20officer%20for%20assessment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20guidelines%20mandated%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eall%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Cspan%3Echildren%20with%20SAM%20were%20referred%20to%20NRCs%20where%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20nutritious%20foods%2C%20medical%20and%20counselling%20support%20was%20also%20expected%20to%20be%20provided.%20This%20is%20one%20of%20the%20major%20changes%20that%20has%20been%20brought%20about%20in%20the%20new%20protocol.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20appetite%20test%2C%20which%20has%20been%20elaborated%20upon%20in%20the%20protocol%2C%20has%20not%20been%20found%20to%20be%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1111%2Ftmi.13360%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%252520appetite%252520test%252520is%252520used%2Cguidelines%252520despite%252520lack%252520of%252520evidence.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereliable%20tool%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20identify%20at-risk%20children%20and%20categorise%20them%20as%20needing%20inpatient%20or%20outpatient%20care.%20A%20child%20may%20not%20feel%20like%20eating%20food%20if%20she%20has%20recently%20had%20a%20sore%20throat%2C%20fever%2C%20nausea%20or%20vomiting.%20It%20could%20be%20that%20the%20child%20does%20not%20like%20the%20smell%20or%20the%20taste%20of%20the%20food%2C%20is%20thirsty%20or%20is%20apprehensive%20about%20the%20teacher%20(or%20parent).%20The%20Anganwadi%20teacher%20is%20expected%20to%20screen%20for%20health%20issues%2C%20when%2C%20in%20reality%2C%20there%20can%20be%20no%20side-stepping%20the%20need%20for%20close%20interaction%20of%20the%20Women%20and%20Child%20department%20with%20the%20Health%20department%20for%20%E2%80%98holistic%20care%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20child.%20Children%20need%20regular%20screening%20health%20checks%20to%20pick%20out%20common%20diseases%20so%20that%20they%20can%20receive%20timely%20care%20and%20this%20is%20non-negotiable.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBurdening%20the%20Anganwadi%20teacher%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20new%20protocol%20for%20malnutrition%20has%20introduced%20several%20categories%20such%20as%20SUW%20(Severe%20Underweight)%2C%20MUW%20(Moderate%20Underweight)%2C%20SAM%20(Severe%20Acute%20Malnutrition)%2C%20MAM%20(Moderate%20Acute%20Malnutrition)%20etc.%20based%20on%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20child%20health%20growth%20standards.%20But%20these%20could%20confuse%20and%20overload%20the%20already%20overwhelmed%20Anganwadi%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eworker%20who%20can%20get%20personally%20penalised%20for%20poor%20nutrition%20status%20of%20children%20as%20though%20it%20is%20an%20individual%20rather%20than%20system%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20workers%20are%20also%20expected%20to%20train%20families%20on%20WASH%20practices%20(safe%20drinking%20water%2C%20personal%20hygiene%2C%20hand%20washing%2C%20use%20of%20toilets%2C%20cleanliness%20of%20home%20and%20surroundings).%20According%20to%20the%20Poshan%20tracker%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.poshantracker.in%2Fstatistics%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estatistics%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20there%20are%20a%20total%20of%2013%2C96%2C957%20Anganwadi%20centres%2C%20with%20only%2011%2C01%2C843%20having%20functional%20toilets%2C%20or%C2%A0%2021%25%C2%A0%20(%202%2C95%2C114)%20Anganwadi%20centres%20without%20a%C2%A0%20functional%20toilet.%C2%A0%20It%20is%20a%20common%20sight%20to%20see%20children%20urinating%20and%20defecating%20outside%20the%20Anganwadi%20centres.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20same%20tracker%2C%20only%2087.5%25%20(i.e.%2012%2C23%2C578)%C2%A0%20Anganwadi%20centres%20have%20drinking%20water.%201%2C73%2C379%20Anganwadi%20centres%20therefore%20do%20not%20have%20drinking%20water.%20If%20each%20Anganwadi%20centre%20caters%20to%20around%2040%20children%2C%20it%20means%20that%C2%A0%2069%2C35%2C160%20children%20are%20exposed%20to%20unsafe%20water%20in%20the%20Anganwadi%20centres.%20Using%20unsafe%20(non-potable)%20water%20for%20drinking%20or%20cooking%20can%20lead%20to%20gastrointestinal%20disease%2C%20pushing%20the%20child%20into%20a%20vicious%20cycle%20of%20malnutrition%20and%20ill-health.%20If%20Anganwadi%20centres%20themselves%20do%20not%20have%20toilets%20and%20drinking%20water%2C%20how%20is%20it%20logical%20for%20these%20centres%20to%20offer%20training%20to%20mothers%20and%20communities%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20these%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F1f9jogHhA_k%3Fsi%3DLNHfK9QbidJaEzKs%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnganwadi%20workers%2C%20who%20not%20only%20cook%20food%20for%20children%20with%20help%20of%20an%20Anganwadi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esahaiyka%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(helper)%2C%20and%20double-up%20as%20a%20primary-level%20teacher%2C%20are%20also%20now%20expected%20to%20visit%20homes%20of%20children%20with%20malnutrition%20to%20provide%20health%20education%20and%20monitor%20progress.%20This%20is%20an%20unrealistic%20expectation%20unless%20arrangements%20are%20made%20for%20one%20teacher%20to%20handle%20the%20Anganwadi%20centre%2C%20while%20another%20makes%20home%20visits.%20Importantly%2C%20many%20of%20these%20Anganwadi%20teachers%20could%20carry%20the%20same%20food%20related%20misconceptions%20and%20prejudices%20as%20shared%20by%20their%20senior%20officials%20to%20the%20community%2C%20thus%20causing%20more%20damage%20than%20good.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAre%20millets%20really%20magical%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMillets%2C%20which%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20promoted%20through%20the%20Anganwadi%2C%20contain%20on%20an%20average%2056-73%20gm%2F100%20gm%20of%20carbohydrate%20and%20none%20of%20the%20millets%20contain%20all%20the%20essential%20amino%20acids%20(EAA).%20The%C2%A0%20%E2%80%98high-fibre%E2%80%99%20in%20millets%20can%20contribute%20to%20decreased%20transit%20time%20in%20the%20gastro-intestinal%20system%20and%20feeling%20of%20fullness%20or%20satiety%20after%20a%20meal%2C%20This%20can%20translate%20to%20feeling%20less%20hungry%20and%20eating%20less%20frequently%20which%20is%20not%20always%20desirable%2C%20especially%20in%20malnourished%20children.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20presence%20of%20%E2%80%98anti-nutrients%20such%20as%20lectins%2C%20phytates%2C%20tannins%20etc.%20can%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fciteseerx.ist.psu.edu%2Fviewdoc%2Fdownload%3Fdoi%3D10.1.1.624.6032%26rep%3Drep1%26type%3Dpdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereduce%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20digestibility%20and%20absorption%20of%20essential%20nutrients%20from%20millets.%20Some%20of%20these%20unwanted%20effects%20can%20be%20reduced%20through%20germination%2C%20fermentation%2C%20pressure%20cooking%2C%20etc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20rush%20to%20push%20for%20millet%20once%20a%20week%20as%20suggested%20in%20the%20protocol%2C%20let%20us%20also%20not%20forget%20that%20many%20of%20these%20foods%20have%20a%20very%20cultural%20context.%20While%20some%20Kannadigas%20would%20drool%20over%20the%20chewy%20and%20sticky%20ragi%20mudde%2C%20it%20could%20be%20a%20potentially%20unpleasant%20experience%20for%20a%20person%20unaccustomed%20to%20it.%20Children%20could%20likewise%20be%20accustomed%20to%20certain%20tastes%20and%20textures.%20Pushing%20them%20to%20eat%20unusual%20foods%20because%20they%20are%20%E2%80%98healthy%E2%80%99%2C%20economical%20or%20good%20for%20the%20climate%20shows%20a%20certain%20insensitivity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ministry%20seems%20to%20be%20enamoured%20by%20an%20initiative%20from%20Assam%20where%20the%20mother%20of%20a%20healthy%20child%20becomes%20the%20%E2%80%98buddy%20mother%E2%80%99%20to%20support%20the%20mother%20of%20a%20malnourished%20child%2C%20as%20per%20the%20new%20protocol.%20In%20reality%2C%20it%20would%20seem%20that%20a%20more%20responsive%20and%20responsible%20%E2%80%98buddy%20government%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour%20for%20children%20and%20families%20either%20struggling%20to%20come%20out%20of%20the%20vicious%20cycle%20of%20malnutrition%20or%20constantly%20being%20pushed%20into%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESylvia%20Karpagam%20is%20a%20public%20health%20doctor%20and%20researcher.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697682641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18165942%2FScreenshot-2023-10-18-at-4.57.27.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fposhan-abhiyan-malnutrition-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Children%20need%20regular%20screening%20checks%20to%20pick%20out%20common%20diseases%20so%20that%20they%20can%20receive%20timely%20care%20and%20this%20is%20non-negotiable.%20Saddling%20the%20Anganwadi%20teacher%20with%20the%20responsibility%20is%20not%20the%20solution.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fposhan-abhiyan-malnutrition-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20Gaza%3A%20Biden%20clinches%20deal%20with%20Egypt%20to%20allow%20aid%22%