e%20storage%20rooms%20beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20would%20take%20another%20nearly%20200%20years%20to%20finally%20confirm%20his%20suspicions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20hidden%20storage%20rooms%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20area%20was%20so%20damaged%20it%20was%20impossible%20to%20enter%2C%20so%20Perring%20had%20no%20way%20of%20knowing%20if%20he%20was%20right.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDecades%20later%2C%20German%20Egyptologist%20Ludwig%20Borchardt%20ignored%20Perring's%20claims%20when%20he%20was%20excavating%20the%20site%20in%20the%20early%201900s.%20If%20he'd%20looked%20closer%2C%20history%20might%20have%20been%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20a%20joint%20Egyptian-German%20team%20working%20to%20restore%20the%20pyramid%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uni-wuerzburg.de%2Fen%2Fnews-and-events%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2Fnews%2Fneue-raeume-in-der-pyramide-von-sahura-entdeckt%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20shown%3C%2Fa%3E%20Perring%20was%20correct.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fancient-civilizations-that-were-hiding-in-plain-sight-2023-1%5C%22%3EUsing%20lidar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20method%20that%20applies%20laser%20pulses%20to%20penetrate%20obstacles%20like%20tree%20canopies%20or%20walls%20to%20see%20what%20lies%20beyond%2C%20the%20researchers%20mapped%20the%20exterior%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkhufu-pyramid-big-room-chamber-void-muons-physics-2017-11%5C%22%3Einterior%20passages%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20chambers.%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETemperature%20changes%2C%20high%20humidity%2C%20and%20windy%20conditions%20have%20helped%20cause%20certain%20parts%20of%20the%20pyramid%20to%20collapse%20over%20the%20centuries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClearing%20some%20of%20the%20rubble%20and%20creating%203D%20maps%20have%20allowed%20the%20researchers%20to%20get%20a%20better%20sense%20of%20the%20structure%2C