0place%20under%20the%20new%20IOC%20leadership%2C%20which%20would%20likely%20mean%20not%20before%202026%2F2027%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20IOC%20spokesperson%20told%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20IOC%20session%20marked%20India%E2%80%99s%20second%20time%20as%20host.%20The%20first%20time%20was%20four%20decades%20ago%2C%20in%201983%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20this%20year%20was%20attended%20by%20global%20sports%20figures%2C%20including%20IOC%20president%20Thomas%20Bach.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20road%20to%20being%20the%20host%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20sports%20event%20is%20not%20so%20simple.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20it%20possible%3F%20A%20varied%20scenario%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20winning%20the%20bid%20to%20host%20the%20Olympic%20games%20is%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20involves%20meticulous%20planning%2C%20strategic%20vision%20and%20rigorous%20evaluation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20timing%20of%20when%20the%20Olympic%20Games%20are%20awarded%20to%20a%20city%20varies%20significantly.%20Tokyo%20and%20Paris%20were%20named%20hosts%20seven%20years%20prior%20to%20the%20event%2C%20whereas%20Brisbane%20secured%20the%202032%20Games%20a%20staggering%2011%20years%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20any%20country%20to%20get%20approval%20to%20host%20the%20games%2C%20the%20country%20needs%20to%20pass%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfeasibility%20study%E2%80%9D%20conducted%20by%20the%20future%20host%20commission%20of%20the%20IOC%2C%20the%20panel%20responsible%20for%20identifying%20and%20recommending%20hosts%20of%20the%20Olympic%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161615%2FInternational-Olympic-Committee-1024x448.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161615%2FInternational-Olympic-Committee-1024x448.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161615%2FInternational-Olympic-Committee-300x131.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161615%2FInternational-Olympic-Committee.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680659%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22368%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBased%20in%20Switzerland%2C%20the%20IOC%20is%20responsible%20for%20organising%20the%20summer%2C%20winter%20and%20youth%20Olympic%20games.%20Photo%3A%20Gzzz%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20there%20are%20nearly%2020%20criteria%20based%20on%20which%20the%20IOC%20decides%20who%20the%20host%20would%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reached%20out%20to%20former%20Croatia%20president%20and%20IOC%20member%20Kolinda%20Grabar-Kitarovic.%20She%20chairs%20the%20future%20host%20commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20reply%2C%20an%20IOC%20spokesperson%20said%20on%20her%20behalf%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20proposed%20masterplan%20of%20any%20interested%20party%20is%20considered%20by%20the%20future%20host%20commission%20during%20continuous%20dialogue%2C%20when%20the%20IOC%20conducts%20a%20feasibility%20study%20to%20help%20the%20interested%20party%20to%20improve%20its%20project%20and%20to%20assist%20the%20IOC%20executive%20board%20with%20its%20strategic%20long-term%20outlook%20and%20decision-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20IOC%20feasibility%20study%20examines%20the%20following%20criteria%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Geopolitical%2C%20socio-economic%2C%20human%20development%20%26amp%3B%20environmental%20factors%3Cbr%3E%20%E2%80%A2%20Vision%20and%20venue%20masterplan%3Cbr%3E%20%E2%80%A2%20Alignment%20with%20existing%20long-term%20development%20plans%2C%20including%20youth%20strategies%3Cbr%3E%20%E2%80%A2%20Envisaged%20sustainability%20and%20legacy%20impacts%3Cbr%3E%20%E2%80%A2%20Political%20and%20public%20support%3Cbr%3E%20%E2%80%A2%20Funding%20strategy%3Cbr%3E%20%E2%80%A2%20Games%20delivery%20capabilities%20and%3Cbr%3E%20%E2%80%A2%20Sports%20event%20experience%2C%20accommodation%2C%20transport%2C%20safety%20and%20security%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20spokesperson%E2%80%99s%20reply%20continued%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThough%20games%20are%20awarded%20to%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3Ecities%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20countries%20are%20often%20interested%20in%20them%20for%20reasons%20that%20go%20beyond%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20India%2C%20Mexico%2C%20Indonesia%20and%20Poland%20have%20officially%20expressed%20their%20interest%20in%20hosting%20the%202036%20Games.%20So%20not%20only%20is%20the%20competition%20fierce%2C%20there%20are%20questions%20on%20what%20is%20happening%20internally%20in%20sports%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMore%20medals%2C%20less%20money%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Youth%20Affairs%20and%20Sports%20has%20nearly%20doubled%20its%20budgetary%20allocation%20from%202014-15%20to%202023-24%2C%20reaching%20approximately%20Rs%203%2C400%20crores.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECentral%20to%20this%20effort%20is%20the%20Khelo%20India%20Scheme%2C%20which%20has%20received%20substantial%20financial%20support%2C%20playing%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20providing%20opportunities%20to%20around%2023%20lakh%20school%20children.%20Much%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20success%20at%20the%20Asian%20Games%20is%20being%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fthe-secret-to-indias-asian-games-success-an-empowering-sports-policy-8978248%2F%5C%22%3Eattributed%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20this%20scheme%2C%20i.e.%20more%20money%2C%20more%20medals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ugly%20Fans%20and%20Honourable%20Sportspersons%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fugly-fans-and-honourable-sportspersons%5C%22%3EUgly%20Fans%20and%20Honourable%20Sportspersons%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20won%20107%20medals%20at%20the%20recently%20concluded%20Asian%20Games%20in%20Guangzhou%2C%20beating%20its%20previous%20best%20of%2070%20medals%20in%20Jakarta%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20Neeraj%20Chopra%20acing%20every%20major%20competition%20since%20the%20Tokyo%20Olympics%2C%20and%20Indian%20sprinters%20%E2%80%93%20namely%20Muhammed%20Anas%20Yahiya%2C%20Amoj%20Jacob%2C%20Muhammed%20Ajmal%20Variyathodi%20and%20Rajesh%20Ramesh%20%E2%80%93%20winning%20gold%2C%20India%20has%20achieved%20unusual%20success%20in%20securing%20medals%20for%20track%20events.%20India%20has%20won%20a%20total%20of%2029%20medals%20in%20athletics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20resurgence%20in%20shooting%2C%20marked%20by%20a%20remarkable%20haul%20of%2022%20medals%2C%20including%207%20golds%2C%20signifies%20a%20significant%20return%20to%20prominence%20in%20the%20shooting%20arena.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Asian%20Games%20has%20brought%20attention%20to%20significant%20disparities%20in%20both%20medal%20counts%20and%20government%20funding%20allocations%20among%20Indian%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGujarat%20failed%20to%20win%20a%20single%20medal%20at%20the%20Asian%20Games.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20pointed%20out%20that%20under%20the%20Khelo%20India%20scheme%2C%20it%20was%20sanctioned%20the%20highest%20funding%20of%20Rs%20608%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20having%2021%20medal%20winners%2C%20had%20secured%20the%20second-largest%20Khelo%20India%20funding%20of%20Rs%20503.02%20crore%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20Haryana%2C%20which%20collectively%20won%2075%20medals%2C%20were%20sanctioned%20less%20than%20Rs%20200%20crore%20combined%20from%20the%20Modi%20government%20under%20the%20Khelo%20India%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E(The%20three%20states%20were%20sanctioned%20Rs%2093%2C%20110%20and%2083%20crore%20respectively.)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20there%20seems%20little%20connection%20between%20medals%20won%20and%C2%A0money%C2%A0allotted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20funding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20220808155004%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2F164.100.24.220%2Floksabhaquestions%2Fannex%2F179%2FAU2614.pdf%5C%22%3Efigures%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20disclosed%20by%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Youth%20Affairs%20and%20Sports%20in%20August%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20discrepancy%20between%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20funding%20and%20its%20performance%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20commendable%20achievements%20of%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20athletes%20with%20limited%20financial%20support%2C%20has%20sparked%20discussions%20about%20the%20need%20for%20a%20more%20transparent%20and%20equitable%20allocation%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fgaps-india-sports-administration-governance%5C%22%3EThe%20Gaps%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20Sports%20Administration%20and%20Governance%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20persistent%20problem%20is%20the%20underutilisation%20of%20allocated%20resources%20and%20infrastructure.%20Despite%20the%20Khelo%20India%20scheme%20receiving%20Rs%20520%20crore%20and%20Rs%20500%20crore%20in%202018-19%20and%202019-20%2C%20the%20actual%20expenditure%20fell%20significantly%20short%2C%20standing%20at%20Rs%20324%20crore%20and%20Rs%20318%20crore%2C%20respectively%2C%20as%20noted%20by%20the%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Human%20Resource%20Development%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20inefficient%20utilisation%20highlights%20graver%20problems%20than%20can%20be%20attended%20to%20by%20a%20mere%20upping%20of%20funds%20pumped%20in.%20They%20point%20to%20systemic%20challenges%20within%20India%E2%80%99s%20sports%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESports%20as%20a%20means%20for%20political%20PR%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20sports%20by%20politicians%20to%20gain%20political%20mileage%20is%20old%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdolf%20Hitler%20utilized%20the%201936%20Olympics%20hosted%20in%20Berlin%20to%20reshape%20the%20image%20of%20Nazi%20Germany.%20Hitler%20and%20Nazi%20officials%20skillfully%20tried%20to%20use%20the%20Olympics%20to%20push%20for%20large%20crowds%20in%20adulation%20of%20Der%20Fuhrer%20and%20the%20idea%20of%20German%20supremacy%20which%20the%20Nazis%20believed%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20Nazi%20Germany%20faced%20international%20criticism%2C%20the%20Olympics%20also%20provided%20the%20perfect%20opportunity%20for%20Hitler%20to%20charm%20global%20counterparts%20and%20portray%20the%20nation%20as%20open-minded%20and%20welcoming.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENoted%20journalist%20and%20author%20Eduardo%20Galeano%2C%20in%20his%20book%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3ESoccer%20in%20Sun%20and%20Shadow%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20writes%20how%20%E2%80%9Cthe%201934%20World%20Cup%20in%20Rome%20was%20an%20elaborate%20propaganda%20operation.%20Mussolini%20attended%20every%20match%2C%20sitting%20in%20the%20box%20of%20honor%2C%20his%20chin%20raised%20toward%20stands%20filled%20with%20black%20shirts.%20The%20eleven%20players%20of%20the%20Italian%20squad%20dedicated%20their%20victories%20to%20him%2C%20their%20right%20arms%20outstretched.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPoliticians%20of%20the%20current%20age%20have%20successfully%20used%20sports%20events%20for%20their%20own%20image-building.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20ride%20in%20a%20%E2%80%98chariot%E2%80%99%20around%20the%20stadium%20named%20after%20him%20in%20Ahmedabad%20with%20Australian%20PM%20Anthony%20Albanese%20got%20panned%20and%20was%20called%20out%20for%20the%20use%20of%20sports%20to%20enhance%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F3fdrQrjAO4w%3Fsi%3Dyr5MF8X6MKO4uNWO%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20sports%20writer%20Gideon%20Haigh%20%E2%80%93%20who%20was%20there%20in%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20stadium%20when%20the%20two%20PMs%20wheeled%20about%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVKStVlWdhuQ%5C%22%3Espoke%20of%20the%20India-Pakistan%20match%20at%20the%20same%20venue%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20sight%20of%20all%20those%20blue%20shirts%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20stadium%20the%20other%20night%20was%20bizarre.%20It%20looked%20like%20a%20Nuremberg%20rally%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20city%3F%20Ahmedabad%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20step%20towards%20a%20possible%20bid%20to%20host%20the%202036%20Olympics%2C%20the%20Ahmedabad%20Urban%20Development%20Authority%20(AUDA)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fahmedabad%2Folympic-village-sardar-patel-sports-enclave-to-now-cover-650-acres%2Farticleshow%2F102665722.cms%5C%22%3Ehas%20earmarked%20an%20additional%2050%20acres%20of%20land%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20part%20of%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20expansive%20initiative%20to%20establish%20cutting-edge%20sports%20facilities%20in%20and%20around%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20ambitious%20project%20aims%20to%20create%20the%20Sardar%20Patel%20Sports%20Enclave%20and%20the%20Olympic%20Village%2C%20pivotal%20components%20for%20hosting%20the%20global%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20cricket%20World%20Cup%20is%20hosted%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20home%20turf%2C%20there%20is%20speculation%20that%20it%20conveniently%20coincides%20with%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20re-election%20campaign%20months%20before%20the%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20BCCI%20under%20Jay%20Shah%20%E2%80%93%20coincidentally%2C%20the%20son%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20home%