20to%20acknowledge%20that%20this%20happiness%20often%20stems%20from%20morally%20questionable%20endeavors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2022%2Fnov%2F11%2Fengland-supporter-conflicted-over-qatar-world-cup-human-rights-record-gay-rights-boycott-tournament%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20in%20a%20recent%20editorial%20on%20%E2%80%98sportswashing%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20writes%20of%20India%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20more%20countries%20it%20claims%20are%20trying%20to%20use%20sports%20in%20ways%20that%20may%20not%20be%20very%20sportsmanlike.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CRealpolitik%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20overlooked.%20Respecting%20different%20cultures%20does%20not%20mean%20abuse%20is%20condoned.%20The%20lure%20of%20the%20arena%20ought%20not%20excuse%20a%20lack%20of%C2%A0moral%C2%A0responsibility.%20Sport%20can%20produce%20great%20public%20happiness%2C%20and%20the%20idea%20that%20only%20the%20ill-intentioned%20would%20censure%20it.%20But%20it%20jars%20to%20know%20that%20the%20pure%20joy%20experienced%20by%20many%20fans%20rests%20on%20the%20fruits%20of%20baseness.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20well%20be%20an%20Indian%20dream%20to%20be%20the%20host%20of%20the%20Olympic%20Games%2C%20but%20this%20dream%20must%20come%20only%20for%20sports%20and%20not%20for%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697641821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18180010%2FModi-at-IOC.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findias-possible-olympic-bid-must-be-for-sports-alone-not-politics%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20history%20of%20sports%20%E2%80%93%20for%20example%2C%20the%20Berlin%20Olympics%20in%201936%2C%20the%20Saudi%20Arabian%20drive%20to%20host%20the%20prestigious%20World%20Golfing%20tournament%20and%20the%20purchase%20of%20European%20Football%20clubs%20%E2%80%93%20drives%20the%20fear%20of%20%E2%80%98sp