ments%20%E2%80%93%20in%20true%20high%20command%20style.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20wipe%20out%20the%20remaining%20pockets%20of%20small%20fiefdoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20appointment%20culture%20is%20an%20old%20Congress%20tradition.%20But%20Congress%20first%20sent%20central%20observers%20to%20the%20states%2C%20tried%20for%20a%20consensus%20candidate%20or%20in%20the%20alternative%20took%20the%20views%20of%20individual%20MLAs.%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20done%20away%20with%20even%20such%20niceties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERegional%20leaders%20of%20all%20parties%20cultivate%20cadre%20who%20are%20personally%20loyal%20to%20them%3B%20in%20turn%2C%20these%20leaders%20provide%20them%20with%20tickets%20and%20funds.%20Such%20fiefdoms%20strengthened%20the%20party.%20Now%20Modi%20wants%20to%20demolish%20these%20vestiges%20of%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20was%20how%20Vijay%20Rupani%20was%20removed%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Felections%2Fassembly-elections%2Fgujarat%2Fnews%2Fbhupendra-patel-takes-oath-as-gujarat-cm-for-second-time%2Farticleshow%2F96168805.cms%5C%22%3Erelatively%20unknown%20Bhupendra%20Patel%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0imposed%20on%20Gujarat%20in%202021.%20Many%20veterans%20protested%20and%20threatened%20to%20keep%20off%20the%20swearing%20ceremony%20but%20meekly%20surrendered%20later.%20Among%20them%20were%20Nitin%20Patel%2C%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%2C%20Gordhan%20Zafadia%20and%20Praful%20Patel.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fconsolidate-patidar-votes-retain-others-support%2Farticleshow%2F86148532.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3EGujarat%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20now%20being%20replicated%20in%20all%20BJP%20strongholds.%20Hereafter%2C%20as%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20it%20will%20be%20Modi%20who%20commands%20the%20cadre%E2%80%99s%20loyalty%3B%20there%20will%20be%20no%20middle%20persons%20like%20Vasundhara%20Raje%