0148B-1024x637.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-582767%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22746%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20addresses%20an%20election%20campaign%20rally.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%2FFile%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBy%20far%2C%20the%20most%20expensive%20pre-election%20Modi%20buildup%20is%20the%20high-tech%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fbefore-ls-polls-modi-govts-massive-outreach-yatra-to-take-central-schemes-to-villages-8957939%2F%5C%22%3EGrameen%20Samvad%20Yatra%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20yatra%20comprises%201%2C500%20raths%20equipped%20with%20GPS%20and%20drones%20%E2%80%93%20yes%20drones%20%E2%80%93%20and%20will%20cover%20over%202.5%20lakh%20panchayats%20across%20the%20country.%20Through%20audio-visual%20displays%2C%20each%20rath%20will%20constantly%20blare%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20speeches%20and%20songs%20in%20praise%20of%20him.%20This%20is%20done%20in%20the%20name%20of%20%E2%80%98educating%E2%80%99%20the%20people%20on%20welfare%20programmes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20specially%20designed%20raths%20with%20flood%20lights%2C%20sparkling%20colour%20and%20large%20official%20entourage%20will%20be%20an%20attraction%20for%20rural%20crowds.%20It%20will%20go%20on%20for%20two%20months%20just%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20To%20pull%20the%20crowds%2C%20cultural%20programmes%20will%20be%20organised%20a%20day%20before%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20rath.%20It%20will%20cover%20three%20panchayats%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20July%20last%2C%2038%20regional%20parties%20attended%20the%20NDA%20meeting.%20Most%20of%20those%20outfits%20do%20not%20have%20enough%20strength%20to%20win%20seats%20on%20their%20own.%20They%2C%20however%2C%20can%20add%20votes%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20kitty%20in%20their%20strongholds.%20To%20that%20extent%2C%20it%20help