rward.%20Several%20people%20here%20are%20converting%20to%20Christianity.%20We%20have%20to%20stop%20this.%20Whether%20it%20is%20through%20reading%20Hindu%20scriptures%20or%20through%20force.%20Hindus%20should%20know%20everything)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Devi%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20propagating%20Hindutva%2C%20Devi%20undertakes%20a%20%E2%80%98noble%E2%80%99%20task%20every%20Friday.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20disciples%20and%20I%20make%20sure%20to%20blast%20%3Cem%3Ebhajans%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20full%20volume%20when%20they%20(Muslims)%20read%20%3Cem%3Eazaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20Friday%20namaz.%20This%20is%20my%20way%20to%20stop%20Islam.%20But%20Christians%20are%20out%20of%20control%2C%20they%20give%20money%2C%20property%2C%20and%20alcohol%20to%20convert%20Hindus%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Devi.%20%E2%80%9CSanatanis%20are%20precious%2C%20they%20should%20be%20trained%20by%20the%20Sangh.%20They%20are%20the%20true%20fighters%20in%20the%20cause.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKumari%20and%20Rana%20agree%20with%20Devi.%20They%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20this%20%E2%80%98training%E2%80%99%20that%20Devi%20suggests%20is%20needed%20to%20keep%20the%20population%20of%20Christians%20and%20Muslims%20under%20check.%20They%20regularly%20consult%20Devi%20and%20take%20her%20suggestions%20to%20the%20local%20RSS%20affiliates%20who%20also%20contact%20Devi%20frequently%20concerning%20mass%20conversion%20conspiracies%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMuslims%20on%20the%20Indo-Nepal%20border%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20met%20with%20Mahender%20Yadav%2C%20the%20supervisor%20of%20Ekal%20schools%20in%20Sitapur%20district.%20Yadav%2C%20who%20took%20Kumari%20and%20Rana%20under%20his%20wings%2C%20believes%20that%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20%E2%80%9Cneed%20to%20be%20shown%20their%20rightful%20place%20in%20society%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20can%20either%20accept%20Hindu%20supremacy%20or%20convert%20to%20Hinduism.%20Ekal%20prepares%20children%20to%20identify%20enemies%20of%20Hinduism%20at%20an%20early%20stage%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20Yadav%2C%20430%20Ekal%20schools%20and%20institutions%20further%20the%20agenda%20of%20radicalising%20students.%20But%20the%20propaganda%20that%20these%20schools%20further%20through%20Tharus%20travels%20beyond%20classrooms.%20Due%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20these%20schools%2C%20Muslims%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20villages%20that%20border%20Nepal%20feel%20vulnerable%20with%20children%20being%20indoctrinated%20to%20hate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBrij%20Bihari%2C%20a%20social%20activist%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Sitapur%20district%2C%20feels%20that%20Tharus%20are%20being%20%E2%80%9Cused%20as%20foot%20soldiers%20in%20the%20border%20districts%20to%20channelise%20Hindutva%20sentiment%E2%80%9D.%20Bihari%20also%20views%20this%20as%20a%20dangerous%20trend%20which%20could%20jeopardise%20the%20lives%20of%20Christians%20and%20Muslims%20along%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20new%20schools%20of%20%E2%80%98hate%E2%80%99%20coming%20up%20every%20day%2C%20Muslims%20like%20advocate%20Pervez%20Iqbal%20feel%20that%20his%20community%20is%20staring%20at%20genocide.%20Iqbal%2C%20who%20is%20a%20local%20activist%20from%20Shravasti%2C%20feels%20that%20Hindutva%20groups%20are%20gaining%20stronger%20ground%20in%20the%20border%20districts%20ever%20since%202014%2C%20and%20even%20more%20since%202019%20%E2%80%93%20coinciding%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIqbal%E2%80%99s%20neighbour%2C%20a%2060-year-old%20Muslim%20man%2C%20Rabiullah%2C%20feels%20that%20with%20tribals%20siding%20with%20Hindutva%20groups%2C%20Muslims%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20leave%20their%20homes%20merely%20for%20being%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CYeh%20log%20kabhi%20bhi%20nikaal%20denge%20humein%2C%20phir%20itni%20mehnat%20ka%20ghar%20do%20paise%20mein%20bech%20kar%20bhaagna%20parhega%2C%20yahan%20haalaat%20wais