-bath_11zon-1697535485.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22459%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20mosaic%20bird%20bath.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMosaic-bird-bath_11zon-1697535485.jpg%20459w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMosaic-bird-bath_11zon-1697535485-224x300.jpg%20224w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMosaic-bird-bath_11zon-1697535485-150x201.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332385%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22614%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20mosaic%20bird%20bath.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERare%20genre%20of%20art%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20single%20parent%2C%20Naomi%20brought%20up%20her%20son%20and%20daughter%20while%20teaching%20English%2C%20History%20and%20Geography%20in%20schools.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMosaic%20art%20was%20mainly%20her%20hobby%20for%20many%20years.%20Her%20keen%20interest%20in%20nature%2C%20gardening%2C%20decor%2C%20and%20DIY%20(do-it-yourself)%20art%20led%20her%20to%20make%20pieces%20for%20her%20own%20home%20followed%20by%20those%20of%20friends%20and%20family.%20She%20was%20not%20confident%20enough%20to%20go%20commercial%20yet.%20It%20was%20her%20son%20who%20encouraged%20her%20to%20do%20so%20in%202018.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYohann%2C%20who%20had%20worked%20in%20hospitality%2C%20sales%20and%20strategy%20for%2010%20years%2C%20was%20initially%20hesitant%20to%20give%20up%20his%20corporate%20job%20and%20join%20the%20venture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20offer%20something%20no%20one%20else%20was%20doing.%20After%20some%20research%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20very%20few%20people%20work%20with%20mosaics%20and%20driftwood%20in%20India.%20It%20is%20a%20rare%20genre%20of%20art.%20But%20it%20is%20also%20a%20very%20niche%20market.%20Few%20people%20understand%20and%20appreciate%20our%20art%2C%E2%8