s%2F2023%2F10%2FSpent-grains-1-1697464267-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSpent-grains-1-1697464267-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332305%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EElizabeth%20upcycles%20%E2%80%98spent%20grain%E2%80%99%20into%20several%20goodies%20such%20as%20cookies%2C%20brownies%2C%20bread%2C%20chapatis%2C%20pizzas%2C%20and%20laddus.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTypically%2C%20if%20a%20microbrewery%20brews%20about%201%2C000%20litres%20of%20beer%20a%20day%2C%20then%20they%20will%20use%20about%20200%20kg%20of%20grains.%20Simply%20put%2C%20about%2012%2C000%20kg%20of%20byproduct%20is%20leftover%20in%20the%20process%20every%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20age-old%20relationship%20between%20brewers%20and%20bakers%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20graduate%20in%20culinary%20arts%20from%20Manipal%20Academy%20of%20Higher%20Education%2C%20Elizabeth%20has%20worked%20as%20a%20chef%20in%20numerous%20restaurants%20worldwide%20including%20Mexico%20and%20California%20for%20nearly%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20always%20been%20drawn%20to%20cooking%20naturally.%20A%20kitchen%20always%20brings%20family%20and%20friends%20together%3B%20an%20interesting%20space%20to%20be%20around.%20A%20kitchen%20is%20a%20place%20that%20can%20build%20perspectives%20on%20food%20and%20the%20supply%20chain%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CBeing%20around%20food%20has%20always%20prompted%20me%20to%20think%20of%20what%20happens%20to%20food%20before%20and%20after%20it%20is%20served%20on%20the%20plate.%20That%20curiosity%20and%20learning%20have%20shaped%20what%20my%20worth%20is%20as%20a%20cook.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20her%20fondness%20for%20cooking%20took%20her%20to%20California%20where%20she%20worked%20with%20food%20historian%20William%2